le=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/KindEditor/attached/image/20170323/20170323151455_4062.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/KindEditor/attached/image/20170323/20170323151507_7343.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">孙逸楷董事长在庆典仪式现场发表重要讲话时说：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“春回大地，万象更新”，在这春风和煦、阳光明媚的美好日子里，我们在这里隆重举行“深圳前海中融国际投资控股集团成立”以及“广东前海秋叶原集团总部乔迁”揭牌仪式。首先请允许我代表董事会向出席今天仪式的各位股东、各位嘉宾表示热烈的欢迎和衷心的感谢!向辛勤工作的全体同仁致以亲切的问候。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/KindEditor/attached/image/20170323/20170323151524_4843.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 20.8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">新集团公司的成立，集团总部的乔迁，翻开了企业发展史上新的一页，我们将以百倍的热情，顽强的斗志，卓有成效地开展工作；以</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 20.8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“不断超越，永创新业”的企业精神为指引，与时俱进，应变求新，兴百年大计，创名优企业;以“高定位，快起步，大市场，大开发，大发展”为目标，争取在5∽10年时间内，围绕“深圳前海中融国际投资控股集团”进行的“投融资以及资产管理”业务、围绕“广东前海秋叶原集团”布局的“线缆生态产业链”产业规模达到1000亿元，为实现企业跨越式发展而不懈努力！</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/KindEditor/attached/image/20170323/20170323151550_7656.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 20.8px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;同时，深感责任重大，任重而道远，殷切期望各位股东、各界朋友一如既往的支持、关心和帮助企业的发展，全体同仁团结一心，众志成城，共创事业的辉煌！</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/KindEditor/attached/image/20170323/20170323151602_2500.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; max-wid