(73, 24, '强强合作，携手共赢！ 热烈欢迎中国安防系统集成科技创新产业联盟参访秋叶原公司！', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180314/5e5253b6b81669a18910b41af5917a42.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“迟日江山丽，春风花草香”。2018年3月9日，农历新春伊始，广东前海秋叶原集团迎来了中国安防系统集成科技创新产业联盟秘书长王达以及广东省东莞市安防协会秘书长郑国慧联合率团的成员单位：<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px;\">深圳达实智能股份有限公司、<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">深圳市欣赛通科技有限公司、</span>深圳市麦驰物联股份有限公司、<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">深圳中电国际信息科技有限公司、</span></span>深圳市齐普光电子股份有限公司、<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px;\">深圳市创捷科技有限公司、</span>安盛信达科技股份公司、深圳市博西尼电子有限公司、深圳市赛为智能股份有限公司、深圳市光头强电子科技有限公司、百年金海科技有限公司、广东安盾安检排爆设备有限公司、深圳昌恩智能股份有限公司、深圳市创显光电有限公司、深圳市国保安防投资发展有限公司、深圳市华安讯科技有限公司、跨越速运集团有限公司、深圳市共济科技股份有限公司、深圳市赛蓝科技有限公司、奥泰斯电子（东莞）有限公司等众多行业大咖联合参访团到访秋叶原集团惠州工业园。<br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180314/a1220c1a3057bf2c67b5feb184b4a8c4.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180314/658c44844252155c1473295e4e95fca0.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180314/2052a43ecd1835727bbb4988e2baafe0.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section><section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">秋叶原公司热烈欢迎产业联盟成员莅临</span></strong></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>在秋叶原集团惠州工业园，广东前海秋叶原集团副总裁，深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司CEO赵海波先生，惠州市秋叶原实业有限公司董事长陈剑德先生、深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司工程事业部总经理孙利敬先生，深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司市场部总经理彭权宗先生等相关负责人热情接待了中国安防系统集成科技创新产业联盟成员单位一行，并详细介绍了秋叶原的发展历程与经营现状、工程项目案例、最新产品与市场优势，众论行业趋势。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 42px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 42px; font-size: 14p