 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>中国安防系统集成科技创新产业联盟一行饶有兴致的参观了秋叶原集团工业园的一系列产品生产车间、研发实验室等，对于展厅呈现的安防系统集成科技创新等产品与技术，联盟王达秘书长给予了很高的评价，表示此番参观体验很新颖、很震撼，也从中学习了很多东西。参观期间，中国安防系统集成科技创新产业联盟单位一行人员与秋叶原集团相关负责人进行了良好的互动，双方在融洽的沟通氛围中达成了诸多共识。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180314/e4c5ddc2fa8b8020ef1c071834d97fd6.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180314/c6fc14115ec537cfeef0c25ae6a73bed.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180314/fd96a139534e5b935e0c6cc0eee81113.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">参观园区环境及优质员工公寓</span></strong></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>参观结束后，中国安防系统集成科技创新产业联盟一行与秋叶原集团高层进行了更深入的交流互动。在交流会上，联盟秘书长王达表示，随着科技的快速发展，安防创新技术日新月异，中国安防系统集成科技创新产业联盟作为服务广大安防企业的协会组织，一定会与时俱进，紧跟潮流，与企业多接触，多交流，紧密合作，更好地服务企业，服务社会。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180314/87f58946911bc141029fc060bd2065b5.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180314/0744dd197ffb58035f7cf402c9890075.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180314/7365e7b5c61d05d22bcd84d517fa0139.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p><br/></p><section><section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">联盟成员参观园区某生产中心</span></strong><br/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>广东前海秋叶原集团副总裁，深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司CEO赵海波先生致辞表示：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; “</span>首先，我谨代表秋叶原集团对中国安防系统集成联盟领导及各位行业大咖的莅临表示热烈的欢迎！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>秋叶原创建于1989年，在集团董事长孙逸楷先生的带领下走过了近30年的发展历程，秋叶原注重产品质量、服务及用户体验，注重于在经营产品的同时经营好人才，更注重于品牌建设及商业诚信，用我们董事长的话说就是：“人之立身，所贵者唯在德行”，意思就是“要做事，先做人”，商业诚信是我们的经营之道，立足之本。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>现在是资源整合和抱团取暖的时代，德国是世界制造强国，提出了工业4.0的发展战略，咱们中国也不甘示弱，提出了智能制造2025，人工智能的时代已经来临，2017年十九大会议的召开，强调把发展经济着力点放在实体经济上，支持民营企业发展，建设制造强国，这一系列的利好政策，我们搞实业的又迎来了我们的春天。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>衷心希望，我们这些行业大咖在中国安防系统集成联盟的领导下，加强沟通、增加互信、资源共享、实现共创共赢！也希望各位领导能给秋叶原的发展提出宝贵意见！<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 22.4px; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">”</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p><br/>