(76, 24, '“视听无界　智造未来＂，秋叶原2018广州国际专业灯光、 音响展圆满谢幕，让我们明年2月再相聚!', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180515/fbac7ed253711b262f39f47949321eb9.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" width=\"827\" height=\"532\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; 秋叶原2018广州国际专业灯光、音响展圆满落幕！ 感谢您的支持，本次展会致力于构筑前瞻性与专业性并举的行业交流平台，紧贴专业影音与IT领域中技术融合的发展浪潮，以“视听无界　智造未来＂为主题，通过举办一系列同期活动，广邀行业精英聚首一堂，共同剖析影音娱乐和会议广播等领域中技术创新、融合与发展等方面的前沿问题，为与会者带来无限新知与商机。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180515/cb07e0ade679ea4b95a441e6d3166ec5.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" width=\"835\" height=\"599\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; 本届展会紧贴我国通讯一体化和技术融合领域强劲的发展势头，强化升级“通讯及会议”及“媒体系统方案”两大专馆，以及精彩纷呈的同期活动，受到业界的一致认可与好评。<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px;\">为行业打造了绝佳的商贸平台，各参展商及买家对展会的新格局赞不绝口！</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180515/1e480b5de1014ac2b2d5112dfed02405.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" width=\"836\" height=\"519\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180515/f9110adcecef5a093bd078e36b638a49.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" width=\"833\" height=\"501\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; 所有来访秋叶原展位的客户都踊跃与我们沟通交流，针对客户提出的专业问题，我们都配有专业的销售人员和技术人员解说。面对我司优秀产品，<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px;\">意向客户</span>关注的是双方之间的合作与配合。针对这些<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px;\">关键的</span>问题，我们有专业的团队、专业的服务意识、积极的响应客户要求，严把产品质量关，推动我们合作更加深入。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180515/3c79e3228ca56913f9b5d0a5a54d695a.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" width=\"840\" height=\"568\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1e