(79, 25, '共建跨界融合平台，共享协同发展荣光——广东前海秋叶原公司热烈祝贺北京大学英国校区启动仪式在英国牛津隆重举行', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2018年3月25日中午，随着红色的幕布徐徐展开，一枚闪亮的北大校徽出现在人们眼前，这标志着北京大学英国校区正式启动，也将北京大学120周年校庆海外庆典推向了最高潮。</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/b3c9ec32e0aaacf7292c0cfa56d972e1.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">北京大学校长林建华</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">北京大学校务委员会副主任</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">汇丰商学院院长海闻</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">中国驻英国大使刘晓明</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">汇丰集团常务总监Noel QUINN共同为校徽揭幕</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;广东前海秋叶原集团作为北京大学汇丰商学院英国校区创始校董成员单位对此表示热烈祝贺，北京大学120周年校庆海外庆典暨北京大学英国校区启动仪式上，中英两国政府代表、学界代表以及北京大学的学生、校友代表参加了活动。</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/c8b2a2623d7f72c046a3472ba0383b94.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">与会嘉宾为校庆纪念雕塑揭幕</span></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/8a3d6e05dff294d1f70aa56a1c98b72c.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">北大校长林建华致辞</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;林建华校长在致辞中指出，当前，与民族共命运的北京大学，也和国家一同进入了改革发展的新时代，站在了新的历史起点上。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;新时代有新的挑战，面对挑战，北大首先要做的是反思。面向未来，北大要明晰目标。在过去的120年，北大以开放包容的姿态，既推动西学东渐，又致力于东学西渐，搭建起中外文明交流互鉴的桥梁。今天的北大，将发扬光荣传统，继续当好中外文明交流交融的使者。北大希望和更多的兄弟高校一道，担负起高等教育引领时代发展的责任，融通中西方文明，努力解决人类社会所面临的共同问题，为人类文明的和谐与共同繁荣贡献新智慧，成为国际社会改革发展的参与者和推动者。</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/4deefc7b25f04a95046545d278f6d531.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">刘晓明大使致辞</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;刘晓明大使在致辞中指出，按照中国纪年方法，120年就是两个甲子，意味着两个“轮回”。站在新“轮回”的起点上，我们不仅要庆祝北京大学历史上的辉煌，更要展望未来的前进方向。从这个意义上讲，北京大学英国校区正式启动，是送给北京大学120周年庆典一份厚重的贺礼。他认为，这其中有三个重要意义：首先，这是传播中国精神的有益尝试。第二，这是讲好中国故事的崭新舞台。第三，这是深化中英教育合作的重要机遇。</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/2dfaa94259dfd8d4bf9cfec667235873.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">从左至右为：Noel QUINN，David BREWER, Keith BURNENT，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">Katharine CARRUTHERS，Frances WOOD，Will NAYLOR分别致辞</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;随后，汇丰集团常务总监Noel QUINN，前伦敦市长Sir David BREWER, 谢菲尔德大学校长Sir Keith BURNENT，伦敦大学学院副校长、伦敦大学学院教育学院孔子学院院长Katharine CARRUTHERS（杜可歆），爱丁堡大学教授、北京大学客座教授Harry DICKINSON，北京大学海外校友代表Frances WOOD（吴芳思），英国高教质量标准署代表Will NAYLOR等先后致辞，表达了对北大120岁生日的祝贺和对新校园启用的祝福。</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/7e64e9a19c051deb55587851c8e802ff.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">诺奖得主：萨金特（左）与戈登（右）发表精彩演讲</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;作为北京大学汇丰商学院英国校区创始校董，广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生在参加2018年1月13日校董会成立大会暨第一届校董会第一次会议时表示，北京大学汇丰商学院英国校区创建之初与广东前海秋叶原集团建立了校、政、行、企深度融合多边共赢的董事会办学体制，创建了紧密对接产业链的应用型人才培养体系，创新了与专业链对接的教学综合改革模式，实施综合改革，培养具有创意、创新和创业能力的“三创”人才，广东前海秋叶原集团愿与各方共建跨界融合平台，共享协同发展荣光。</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/7205a32456ead6aad877c688ebbc014e.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong>广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生参加</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong>北大英国校区校董会成立大会暨第一次会议</strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/bef5050a56e623c0f031c9b8030e207d.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/e99de797965b5a31a8d177a98361fa20.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong>广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;当今时代是一个资源整合、跨界融合的时代，更是一个开放合作、互惠共赢的时代。校企间的合作搭建起了教育链、人才链与产业链、创新链融合发展的全新平台，必将为企业转型发展注入新的强劲动力和提供有力的人才和智力支撑。秋叶原集团将始终秉持“开放包容、合作共赢”理念，围绕智能生活产业发展建设创新性、交叉性、实用性的行业特色和产业集群，全力推动人才培养供给侧和产业发展需求侧全方位融合，全力构建校企多方联动、产学研深度融合、资源平台共建共享协同发展新格局，一起携手共铸辉煌、共赢未来。</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/0ce0da7ce1609b6489378d4d4f296400.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">北京大学汇丰商学院英国校区创始校董纪念碑揭幕</span></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/8c4d286a6b5a8c47dc9b732a36526f3c.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">北京大学英国校区风景</span></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/978f04a667a86a2380404c291476e37d.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">北大汇丰商学院大楼</span></p><p><br/></p>', 5, 0, 1, 118, NULL, NULL, '2018-03-28 00:00:00', '2018-05-22 17:55:58', '/upload/image/20180516/5ca06fba333ba18d0d26bbf4583aff32.jpg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(80, 24, '关于秋叶原性能升级与导入新VI体系的通知', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180524/10f23e87c73c24d76784ede6750ad0f4.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p>', 5, 0, 1, 118, NULL, NULL, '2018-05-24 09:41:23', '2018-05-24 11:40:15', '/upload/image/20180524/36d239f8de2c6eceef5e85a0bddf95e3.jpg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN');
INSERT INTO `news` (`id`, `news_cate_id`, `title`, `short_title`, `content`, `admin_id`, `count`, `is_show`, `sort`, `start_time`, `end_time`, `create_at`, `update_at`, `pic`, `pics`, `seo_title`, `seo_keyword`, `seo_description`, `platform`, `lang`) VALUES
(81, 25, '迎接5G智能化新生活，你需要提早布置高速率网线。', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 26px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">移动通信系统从</span>1G发展到4G，现有网络是一个2G/3G/4G共存，包含多种无线制式的复杂</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 26px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">网络。</span>5G接入网将会是一个满足多场景的多层异构网络，能够容纳已广泛应用的各种无线接入技术和5G新空口多种接入技术。5G网线网络架构将具有更加灵活的网络拓扑，以及更智能高效的资源协同能力。</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180607/7b3ee7217d5aff6922663e4c5df0a6b7.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 26px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">为了满足互联网</span>+业务快速发展需求，5G无线通信网络不再仅仅解决人与人的通信问题，而是包含了人和机器、机器和机器之间的生态信息系统。根据5G网络业务特点，5G典型覆盖场景包括室外广域覆盖、室内热点覆盖、低功耗数据采集、低时延物联网控制。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 26px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">近年来，每逢大小的消费电子或移动通讯展会，</span>5G都会成为众所瞩目的焦点。无论是攻克5G基础科技的企业、网络运营商，还是智能终端厂商都对5G抱有极高的热情。虽然5G最快可在2019年走进现实，但对于普通用户来说，距离“看得见”和“摸得着”还需要一段时间。那么，作为普通消费者，我们对5G可以抱以什么样的期待呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 26px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">要知道，</span>5G带来的不止是更快的网络，它将会颠覆我们连接体验的方方面面。至于具体会如何影响我们的生活？最近，美国高通公司（以下简称高通）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 26px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">得益于</span>5G低功耗多频段低时延的特点，它能将所有交通设施都连接在一起，并保持实时连动。例如，摄像监控看到地面脏了，会立即反馈给智能清洁车处理；还有地面温度监测器监测到地面温度过高时，会立即反馈给路边的洒水装置，接着洒水给地面降温。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 26px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">简单来说，就是</span>5G让所有交通设施实现高速、多频段和低时延的网络连接，它们不再是单独工作，而是可以相互连动。这样一看，是不是很酷？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 26px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">实际上，还有更酷的事情。高通这段短片演示了</span>5G给一条街道带来的变化，如果往更大的范畴来看，5G甚至能让整个城市连动起来。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 13px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">5G将打破智能化生活的门槛</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 26px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">生活智能化，是近年来消费电子和移动通讯行业发展的一个重要方向。我们可以看到智能穿戴、智能家居、</span>VR/AR和无人驾驶一个接着一个地走热，甚至现在连门锁都在搞智能化。智能化指的是将传统的硬件产品进行智能化改造，并赋予它们连接能力，也就是“智能+连接”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">为我们现有的生活再来来一个更智能、更便捷的体验。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 26px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">毫无疑问，大家都希望</span>5G能快点到来，为各行业带来更多机会与变革</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">广大网民将随时</span>“被”迈进5G新时代。为了不被淘汰，万变不离其宗，首<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">要</span>就是做好基础硬件铺设准备。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 13px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">主动迎接</span>5G新生活，远眺眼光换便捷</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 13px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180607/3b15f0235013b444973e26ae63e14047.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 26px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">首先，</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 26px;\">5G带来的是超高速率的网络，下行峰值速率可达20 Gbps，而4G的下行峰值速率为千兆级（</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 26px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1000Mbps</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 26px;\">），5G的速率足足是4G的20倍。这从纯粹的理论角度来说，下载同样大小的文件，5G的下载时间可以减少至4G的1/20左右。</span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180607/5d523d5fa3c178184c5514e3c9c2922e.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 26px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">SO,超五类以下网线终将像2G网络一样面临淘汰，但是连接的网线并不是可以轻易更换，工程用线、家庭用线、机房建设等工程浩大、更换成本高的投入项目，必须超前消费，提前预留满足衰减小、串扰小、抗干扰</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;;\">高速网线。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><section><section><section><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-wo