(87, 21, 'New pattern of intelligent new era marketing warmly congratulate choseal on its successful strategic', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180801/a7b9a262676cc202479fd1573c448b11.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;On 29-30 July 2018, the &quot;meeting of strategic partners of the domestic marketing department of Shenzhen choseal Industrial Co., Ltd.&quot; was successfully held in Shenzhen, Wanyue grand cloud sky hotel in Shenzhen, on the theme of &quot;new pattern of intelligent new era marketing&quot;. Mr. Sun Yikai, President of Guangdong Qianhai choseal group, President of Shenzhen choseal Industrial Co., Ltd., Mr. Sun Yichen, vice chairman of Guangdong Qianhai choseal group, Mr. Chen Jiande, chairman of Huizhou choseal Industrial Co., Ltd., Mr. Chen Jianfa, general manager of the Shenzhen City, choseal Industrial Co., Ltd. Responsible person, Huizhou choseal Industrial Co., Ltd. production department responsible person attended the meeting, the strategic partners were invited to participate in this meeting.</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180801/cc7afb6617d5f79e0a77fa394a6876e0.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p>At the beginning of the conference, Mr. Sun Yikai, President of Guangdong Qianhai choseal group and President of Shenzhen Akihabara Industrial Co., Ltd., delivered a speech at the conference.</p><p>Distinguished partners, ladies and gentlemen, Hello! Today, we gather together in Shenzhen, the central city of the Great Bay District of Guangdong, Hongkong and Macao, and hold a grand meeting of the strategic partners of the domestic marketing department. Here, on behalf of the board of the akiiyuan group, I would like to express my warm greetings and sincere greetings to all the partners and new and old friends invited to this meeting.</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"></span><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180801/296bffba7a568999ca1d6b118b92bd50.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong>Address by Mr. Sun Yikai, chairman of choseal group, Qianhai, Guangdong</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;The theme of this meeting is &quot;the new marketing pattern of intelligent new era&quot;, which is coming from the new era of 5G, artificial intelligence, smart home and intelligent manufacturing. In a new round of real estate regulation, Sino US trade war, raw material price fluctuation, competition homogeneity, electric business impact and so on, the traditional marketing model It has restricted the pace of the development of the company. If the company does not deepen the reform and opens the pattern of innovation, it will face the crisis of market development. Therefore, the company&#39;s determination to promote the layout of the reform is unswerving. In the coming year, it will accelerate the implementation of the overall development plan of the company.</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180801/158529bcd8e84d34b55cf4deb524d2e6.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;\">Mr. Sun Yichen, Vice Chairman of Guangdong Qianhai choseal Group</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;\"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;The development and operation of the business city platform technology is the most important part of the company&#39;s development in the next 30 years. It is an important support to create a new pattern of marketing. It is a win-win platform for the company to build for the general partners. It is the development of the business with the partners as the main body in the platform, and the company provides value-added services. The future business city will create an intelligent life experience Pavilion by integrating high quality brands, design experts, supply chain and financial products in the intelligent life industry, providing consulting design, product supply and online products of various kinds of digital transmission, IT digital connection, intelligent security, intelligent transportation, intelligent home, system integration and so on. Experience one-stop service and cross-border import and export business, committed to become the industry&#39;s leading intelligent life industry operating platform.</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180801/8a36cde77d7b21fb7d4bb8804eb0b56f.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;\">Mr. Zhou Yizhong, regional manager of marketing department in choseal</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;In the new product development planning, the company will rely on the advantage of the choseal brand, and introduce the advanced technology development of the advanced products around 5G, artificial intelligence, smart home and system integration industry. At the same time, the company will speed up the construction of the supply chain department and integrate the series of products with the top of the high end. Add value products, take the best quality route.</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180801/ec4a72cdcfbe1cf61abfe60578319845.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;In the partnership system, the company will unswervingly carry out the strategic partner system, take turns in the general manager system, the senior executives attach the regional management system, share the bonus with the strategic partners, and hope that more partners will join the team of strategic partners. At the same time, the company will improve the overall management system and rule by law. To establish a modern enterprise management system.</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180801/7e6d1b3a73573088f525ba80b2d12298.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">All the partners, the road of reform is tortuous and the direction of progress is bright. As long as we work together with our minds, emancipate our minds, continue to carry forward the spirit of hard struggle and continue to forge ahead, we will certainly win the final victory of the reform.</span><span class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;In the coming year, the company is willing to work with the partners, brainstorm, seek common development, create a better future, share the original development results of Akiba.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"></span><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180801/e2192108ccbb8cccf4e0a9156aa94bd7.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;\"></span></strong></p><p>The former Committee of the security products expert committee of the Ministry of public security,</p><p>Special members of the electric cable and cable bid committee,</p><p>Mr. Chen Jiande, Chairman of Huizhou Choseal Industrial Co., Ltd.</p><p>Speech on &quot;5G Knowledge and Cable Development Frontier Technology Sharing&quot;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180801/d5f5f5489ff623686bb3b3eda4091c1d.JPG\" title=\