(90, 14, 'Help others, love and devotion', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/797e12a8b3c4c35106fdba0b0e7d219f.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>In the afternoon of June 3rd, choseal &quot;love fund&quot; promotion conference was held in the multi function conference center of choseal group, and it was officially announced that choseal &quot;love foundation&quot; was established. choseal love fund has a initial contribution of more than 50 members. Mr. Sun Yikai, chairman of the chairman of Guangdong Qianhai choseal group, Shenzhen choseal Industrial Co., Ltd., Mr. Sun Yichen of the company director, Mr. Pang Yunjie, the vice president of the company, and Yang Xiaojian, the chief executive of the administrative human center, attended the meeting and delivered a speech. choseal &quot;love foundation&quot; promotion conference clearly defined the responsibility and future implementation details of the love fund, which marks the official opening of the love foundation of choseal &quot;love foundation&quot;.</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/16c1ed73e097197f32c2f37284b224d5.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>Caring for public welfare is the cause of the whole country and the whole nation working together and operating together, and is the responsibility of the whole society. It is a kind of heart, but also the cultivation and transmission of love. The &quot;love foundation&quot; of choseal will take the public welfare as an unshirkable responsibility. In the development of the company, all the employees and other people who need help from the company are actively responsible for the social responsibility, and the &quot;love foundation&quot; is set up to contribute their strength to the public welfare. The establishment of choseal &quot;love foundation&quot; provides a more convenient channel for helping employees and their families to solve major diseases, accidents and family life difficulties. It also increases employees&#39; sense of belonging to the company, creates a good corporate culture and a warm working atmosphere, and gives full play to the enterprise maintenance staff. The role of personal interests, solidarity and mutual assistance, poverty alleviation and poverty relief.</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/4e0412579b3eda6c6cc813aa28a7961c.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>Love, is a beautiful term, but also the Akihabara company has always adhered to the cause. The company established a love fund to help employees very early, although it played a certain role, but because of the lack of formal process system and mature management mechanism, the function of rescue is also limited. Now, the management system of choseal love fund has been perfected, the management and use of choseal love fund are standardized, and the love fund will play a more active role and help more people.</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/442eef6514d95e23d8ce84036135d505.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>Mr. Sun Yikai, the chairman of the company, on behalf of the board of directors of the company, promotes the love fund of Akihabara to all the staff, hoping that everyone will actively and enthusiastically participate in the donation activities of the love fund. With practical action to show support for the activities, the board of directors of the company donated 50000 yuan to choseal love fund, and Mr. Sun Yichen, the director of the company, promised to donate RMB 4000 yuan a month. Initial members of Akihabara Fund more than 50 people later lined up to donate enthusiastically. The atmosphere at the conference was warm and full of love.</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/4737f57b7dc93c7e0c949e0923d642cb.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>The power of charity is great. It can not only help people overcome difficulties, build confidence and courage in life, but also make people good, care for others and give back to society. The establishment of choseal love fund is to disseminate the traditional virtues of &quot;helping people and enjoying devotion&quot; in the company, so that every employee of choseal can pass on and inherit love and happiness, and get a better life guarantee, so that each of us can feel the warmth of the akiiyuan family. Give roses, your hands are fragrant; give love, harvest hope. Let&#39;s join hands to care for and support the cause of Akihabara Love Fund and help everyone in need.</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', 5, 0, 1, 255, NULL, NULL, '2018-08-09 16:21:13', '2018-08-14 10:26:52', '/upload/image/20180809/efc9c5ce11e06cc15cee4c39087f6853.png', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(91, 14, 'Public welfare and great love- the donation ceremony', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p>In the morning of July 14th, &quot;enthusiasm for public welfare and great love,&quot; the donation ceremony of &quot;love foundation&quot; of akiara was held at the Nanshan District branch of Shenzhen Public Security Bureau in Guangdong and Hai police station.</p><p><br/></p><p>In June 15, 2016, Chen Qixu, a police officer at the Nanshan District branch of the Shenzhen Municipal Public Security Bureau, was killed by the police officer of the Guangdong police station. He used the sweat and life to maintain the peace of the city and the community in Shenzhen. He once fought the scene of the law enforcement. He had been a sharp knife to the criminals. Golden shield, accumulated labor into illness, dragging pain, unswervingly defend the city&#39;s people&#39;s lives and property security! He is an unknown hero police, his feelings have been repeatedly reported by Shenzhen television and Shenzhen city newspaper, causing extensive attention from people of all walks of life and local media.</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/071887bce616075bc30f644ca118a632.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p><p>After learning this report from the media, the love foundation of Shenzhen timiyuan Industrial Co., Ltd. was deeply touched by the heroic deeds of Chen Qixu police officers. Chen&#39;s work was very serious. He had long struggled in the front line with all kinds of criminal forces. It faithfully fulfilled the duties of a people&#39;s police and was a good policeman of the party and the people. He died on business, leaving his unemployed wife and junior high school graduate son dependent. To this end, our love foundation of akiara, in line with the spirit of &quot;help for happiness and love and devotion&quot;, has made the initiative to connect with the Shenzhen Nanshan District Guangdong and the Guangdong police station, expressing the willingness to contribute to the Chen Qixu family of the first level police officer who was lost to duty and to help his son to continue his study.</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/1ac4a40e66ca597bf125b6152d69363d.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p><p>Zhang Yonghua, director of the Nanshan District branch of the Shenzhen Municipal Public Security Bureau, director Xie Zhuangbo, director of the administrative human center of Shenzhen choseal Industrial Co., Ltd. and director of the &quot;love foundation&quot; management committee, Mr. Yang Xiaojian, attended the donation ceremony and made a speech successively. Ms. Chen Qixu, the first level police widow, Huang Xueling Donations, both sides signed the donation agreement, Shenzhen Nanshan District Guangdong and the sea police station for thanks akiara &quot;love foundation&quot; of the charity, special to akiara &quot;love foundation&quot; issued a &quot;heart of public welfare, great love no frontier&quot; bronze plaque.&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/cd3a165e1d535d7faf65eadab30d05d0.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>During the connection with the Nanshan District local police station of Shenzhen Municipal Public Security Bureau, the &quot;love foundation&quot; of choseal came to Nanshan District branch of Shenzhen Municipal Public Security Bureau to understand the heroic deeds of Chen Qixu police officers and the related circumstances of their martyrdom. When akiara &quot;love foundation&quot; was informed of the report, the first time was contacted with the Guangdong police station and completed all the connection work on the donation in a short period of one or two weeks.</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/3a4fae2b066be9443a4102527e44cb0e.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>On the morning of July 14, choseal &quot;Love Foundation&quot; formally donated to the family members of Chen Qixu, a first-class police officer from Guangdong-Hai Police Station of Nanshan Branch of Shenzhen Public Security Bureau. The donation is as follows: 1. Commitment to subsidize Chen&#39;s son from high school to university graduation monthly basic living expenses of RMB 1,000 yuan. 2. Commitment to subsidize the study of officer Chen&#39;s son every semester (reimbursement shall be made on the basis of the amount of the invoice or payment document actually paid for each semester). 3. The funding period will take effect from September 1, 2016.</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/c97042b4d12b0754da7f1786b3a6d2b7.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>Zhang Yonghua, director of the Nanshan District branch of the Shenzhen Municipal Public Security Bureau, on behalf of the entire police officer, expressed heartfelt thanks and lofty respect to the charity action of choseal &quot;love foundation&quot; to contribute to the family of Chen Qixu police officers. He said that the love and charity organizations of all walks of life, represented by the &quot;love foundation&quot; of choseal, uphold the good tradition of the Chinese nation&#39;s charity and charity, the heart of the people&#39;s police, the enthusiasm of the public, the great love, and the transmission of positive energy.</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>We firmly believe that the public spirit of &quot;love and devotion&quot; of &quot;love foundation&quot; of Shenzhen choseal Industrial Co., Ltd. will be widely spread and flourished with the core values of &quot;loyalty, justice, for the people and dedication&quot; of the Shenzhen Municipal People&#39;s police.</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', 5, 0, 1, 255, NULL, NULL, '2018-08-09 16:23:47', '2018-08-14 10:22:54', '/upload/image/20180809/0196146ffc447cbe0b8d4ec5ba68762f.jpg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(92, 17, 'The 9th \"Choseal Cup\" Men\'s Basketball League', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p>In order to give full play to the team cooperation ability among the employees of choseal group, enrich the style and entertainment of the staff, strengthen the cooperation and exchange among the various functional departments, strengthen the cohesiveness of the team and show the spirit of the staff of choseal, the Ninth &quot;choseal Cup&quot; men&#39;s basketball match was held in the autumn of Qianhai, Guangdong in June 23rd. The production base of Huizhou is officially opened!</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/cb1799a9904afd02d3b2ad0a2d01c25f.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br/></p><p>At 18:00 p.m., the opening ceremony of the basketball league was presided over by Xiang Ronghua, manager of the group administration department. With a powerful opening music and the opening ceremony of 7 contingent of contestants, executive HR Director Yang Xiaojian delivered an impassioned opening ceremony, emphasizing that choseal group&#39;s basketball game is an important event to enhance corporate culture and team cohesion and to host the success of the event. Good wishes.</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/dbd04413f68e49c4b2475fcb6082a6fd.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/>&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/37f89f4060d7eef99921c218d142a1eb.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>In order to ensure the &quot;fairness&quot;, &quot;fairness&quot; and &quot;openness&quot; of the competition, the referee and the representatives of the participating athletes take oaths on the stage respectively. Finally, Peng Quanzong, the general manager of the marketing department, announced the opening of the 9th &quot;choseal cup&quot; men&#39;s basketball league.</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/e2d4d25bf92cffbc9fb55672232eb991.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br/></p><p>The opening competition was started by the marketing center team and the R&amp;D center team. The atmosphere was warm and exciting, and the competition reached its climax quickly. Competitors with a &quot;higher, faster, stronger&quot; spirit of sports competition Akihabara Group should have the indomitable spirit of struggle.</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/93afd43f753f6112770aa867fcf4dd8d.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br/></p><p>The whole game is bustling and rhythmic. The exciting competition process won the audience&#39;s cheers and warm applause. True competition out of style, competition out of friendship, competition out of the level, fully demonstrates the Qiuyeyuan Group staff&#39;s good quality and the spirit of fighting.</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/7b2d62e7e433ca667e491749d4dbb94d.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/3cfa158628c357fac65d2e0638dea006.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>The success of the &quot;choseal cup&quot; men&#39;s basketball league tournament has further activated the amateur cultural life of the vast number of staff and fostered a corporate culture. In the company, the company has created a good atmosphere of enhancing friendship, training and gathering strength, promoting the wide development of all members of the fitness movement in choseal group and promoting the steady promotion of the construction of enterprise culture.</p><p>I believe the next games will be more exciting, please look forward to!</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180131/f76ba1204c70554aa65e6aaa5a6f49a6.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p>', 5, 0, 1, 255, NULL, NULL, '2018-08-09 16:26:03', '2018-08-14 10:12:10', '/upload/image/20180809/4a231b7eeb8200506808a2717bacb54a.jpg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
