(94, 26, 'Co construction of cross boundary integration platform, sharing the cooperation development glory', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; At noon on March 25, 2018, with the red curtain slowly unfolding, a shining University Emblem appeared in front of the people. This marked the official start of the British campus of the Peking University and the high tide of the overseas celebration of the 120th anniversary Peking University.</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/b3c9ec32e0aaacf7292c0cfa56d972e1.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Lin Jianhua, President of Peking University</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Deputy director of the school affairs committee of Peking University</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">HSBC Dean of the business school</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Liu Xiaoming, China&#39;s ambassador to Britain</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Noel QUINN, executive director of HSBC Group, jointly unveiled the logo</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Guangdong Qianhai choseal group, as a founding member of the British School District of the Peking University HSBC School of Commerce, warmly congratulated it. At the ceremony of the 120th Anniversary overseas celebration of the Peking University and the starting ceremony of the Peking University UK campus, the representatives of the Chinese and English governments, the representatives of the academia and the students and alumni representatives of the Peking University Activity.</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/c8b2a2623d7f72c046a3472ba0383b94.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">The guests opened the celebration sculpture.</span></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/8a3d6e05dff294d1f70aa56a1c98b72c.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">Speech by Lin Jianhua, President of Peking University</span></p><p><br/></p><p>In his speech, President Lin Jianhua pointed out that, at present, the Peking University, with the common destiny of the nation, also entered a new era of reform and development with the state, and stood on a new historical starting point.</p><p>There are new challenges in the new era. In the face of these challenges, the first thing Peking University should do is to reflect. Facing the future, Beida should make clear goals. In the past 120 years, Peking University, with an open and inclusive attitude, has not only promoted the spread of Western learning to the east, but also committed itself to the spread of eastern learning to the west, thus building a bridge for exchanges and mutual learning between Chinese and foreign civilizations. Today&#39;s Peking University will carry forward the glorious tradition and continue to be a good messenger of cultural exchanges between China and foreign countries. Beijing University, with more brothers and universities, is responsible for the responsibility of higher education to lead the development of the times, to integrate the Chinese and Western civilizations, to work hard to solve the common problems faced by the human society, to contribute new wisdom to the harmony and common prosperity of human civilization and to become a participant and promoter of the development of the international community.</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"></span><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/4deefc7b25f04a95046545d278f6d531.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">Ambassador Liu Xiaoming&#39;s speech</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Ambassador Liu Xiaoming pointed out in his speech that according to the Chinese chronological method, 120 years is two Jiazi, which means two &quot;reincarnations&quot;. Standing on the starting point of the new &quot;reincarnation&quot;, we should not only celebrate the brilliant history of Peking University, but also look forward to the future direction of development. In this sense, the official launch of the British campus of Peking University is a great gift to the 120th anniversary celebration of Peking University. In his view, there are three important meanings: first, it is a useful attempt to spread the Chinese spirit. Second, this is a new stage for telling Chinese stories. Thirdly, this is an important opportunity to deepen Sino-British educational cooperation.</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/2dfaa94259dfd8d4bf9cfec667235873.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">From left to right: Noel QUINN, David BREWER, Keith BURNENT.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Katharine CARRUTHERS, Frances WOOD, Will NAYLOR respectively address</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Subsequently, Noel QUINN, Managing Director of HSBC Group, Sir David BREWER, former Mayor of London, Sir Keith BURNENT, Vice-Chancellor of University of London, Katharine CARRUTHERS, Dean of Confucius Institute, School of Education, University of London, Professor of Edinburgh and Visiting Professor of Peking University, Harry DICKIN SON, Frances WOOD (Wu Fangsi), the representative of Peking University overseas alumni, and Will NAYLOR, the representative of British Higher Education Quality Standards Agency, delivered speeches to congratulate Peking University on its 120th birthday and to wish the new campus a success.</span><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/7e64e9a19c051deb55587851c8e802ff.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">Nobel laureates: Sargent (left) and Gordon (right) give excellent speeches</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;As the founding director of the UK campus of the HSBC Business School of Peking University, Mr. Sun Yikai, chairman of Guangdong Qianhai choseal Group, said at the inaugural meeting of the board of trustees and the first meeting of the first board of Trustees on January 13, 2018 that the UK campus of the HSBC Business School of Peking University was established at the beginning of its establishment with the Guangdong Qianhai choseal Group. The school-running system of the board of directors, which integrates politics, banking and enterprises into a multilateral and win-win situation, has created an applied talent training system closely linked to the industrial chain, innovated the teaching comprehensive reform mode linked to the professional chain, implemented comprehensive reform, and trained the &quot;three creative&quot; talents with creativity, innovation and entrepreneurial ability. The group is willing to work together with all parties to build cross platform integration platform to share the glory of collaborative development.</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/7205a32456ead6aad877c688ebbc014e.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mr. Sun Yikai, Chairman of Guangdong Qianhai Qiuyeyuan Group, attended</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Founding Meeting and First Meeting of the British Campus Board of Peking University</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/bef5050a56e623c0f031c9b8030e207d.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/e99de797965b5a31a8d177a98361fa20.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong>Mr. Sun Yikai, chairman of the Qianhai choseal group, Guangdong</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Today&#39;s era is an era of resource integration and cross-border integration, but also an era of open cooperation, mutual benefit and win-win situation. The cooperation between schools and enterprises has set up a new platform for the integration and development of education chain, talent chain, industry chain and innovation chain, which will inject new strong impetus and provide powerful talents and intellectual support for the transformation and development of enterprises. Qiuyeyuan Group will always adhere to the &quot;open, inclusive, win-win cooperation&quot; concept, around the development of intelligent life industry to build innovative, cross-cutting, practical industry characteristics and industrial clusters, and strive to promote the supply side of talent training and industrial development demand side all-round integration, and strive to build a multi-faceted school-enterprise, industry-university-research depth Fusion, resource platform construction, sharing and new pattern of coordinated development, work together to create a brilliant and win-win future.</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/0ce0da7ce1609b6489378d4d4f296400.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">The monument to the founding of the British campus of the HSBC School of Commerce, Peking University</span></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/8c4d286a6b5a8c47dc9b732a36526f3c.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">Peking University English Campus Landscape</span></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180516/978f04a667a86a2380404c291476e37d.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">Beijing University of Huifeng business school building</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', 5, 0, 1, 255, '2022-05-03 02:16:41', '2022-05-03 02:16:41', '2018-08-10 11:13:23', '2018-08-14 10:08:46', '/upload/image/20180810/d2b507164f1bc1fea577b378b43e4bdb.jpg', '[]', '', '', '', 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(95, 23, '大灾无情，秋叶原有爱！秋叶原集团志愿者协会携手灾区人民共克时艰，撑起新希望！', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/292abcf4efc85063b33339d9e3112402.jpg\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \">潮汕地区因连续暴雨，使得潮汕地区严重水灾，个别区域水位高达2米。截止9月2日，汕头市6个区县55个镇（街道）受灾，农作物受灾面积21.39万亩，受灾人数达近百万人。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/b9df7ede5109713e78a9f7f19e1437c5.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>五年前台风“尤特”带来的疮痍还历历在目；五年后，暴雨再次冲垮了潮汕人民的家园。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;水灾无情，狰狞着撕扯着一个个鲜活的生命，咆哮着将潮汕这片土地撕裂，将人们的心血再次吞没。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"></span><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/cf7cef56148bdb1920ee344329de6feb.png\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/6a965ec624cde857e02d968b859e9bea.jpg\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 水灾无情，但人性的温暖、同胞的情谊，温暖的送达无处不在。在潮汕人民迅速、果断地奋力自救的同时，来自四面八方的援助力量也在赶来。</span><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/737736e73a72a4f52c29fe5e4f37916c.jpg\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 心系灾区的广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生和夫人杨明华女士，针对灾区情况联系调度收集、采购大米、食油、牛奶、防蚊虫百草油等缺乏物资。</span><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/843c2d666eea3d278a6586ab35aafa6b.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/91f0b632c0742f991ef8aeb8c067a59f.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/22049863451287b94534a49e6d09d7b7.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 9月2日连夜完成物资收集和打包，凌晨秋叶原志愿者成员即刻装车，身穿“秋叶原集团志愿者协会”红马甲的志愿者从秋叶原制造基地出发，第一时间奔赴灾区现场。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/a628700e08c6b6aa410735b1c5e71edd.jpg\"/><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/bdffb36566f226dc6ee82c0c63d3301b.jpg\"/><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/c27083f8f4d48176954f4d88a96c9b8a.jpg\"/><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/00d07a16cd7614fae77487191b01db61.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 76, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px;\">秋叶原集团志愿者在潮南区陈店镇洋内村赈灾点发放物资<img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/ef113d9bc848c0699a1848c097d647a3.jpg\"/></span></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 76, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 76, 0); font-size: 12px;\">洋内村村长与秋叶原集团志愿者惜别</span></strong></span></span></strong></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/92647ca1608e70bd760eb5ad82d25503.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 个人的力量是渺小的，却又是伟大的！我们感恩秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生这样一位有责任有担当有情怀心怀大爱的企业家，感恩董事长夫人杨明华女士奉行大爱，用实际行动号召带领秋叶原集团志愿者助人为乐，诠释温情为灾区人民带去一片阳光，为秋叶原人带来有温度的无声力量。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/2e7b37aaf287833280a82bf6fb6a15d0.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20180906/0872c67b5f57d6d72e5a71e446fce557.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p>', 5, 0, 1, 118, NULL, NULL, '2018-09-04 00:00:00', '2018-09-06 09:35:01', '/upload/image/20180906/ba3f74b7e85e5f24ca004a90d0ea67b8.jpg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(96, 24, '秋叶原5G网线,智领5G新时代！2018北京安博会与您一起开创新未来！', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/4c90c877f571e99f4f41d44037c76ec9.jpg\"/><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;备受瞩目的2018年中国国际社会公共安全产品博览会(以下简称“2018北京安博会”)于10月23-26日在中国国际展览中心新馆隆重召开。<br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/f366b5e9d3be6e960d1b78b42609d149.png\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;本届安博会以“构建平安中国、服务一带一路、创新智能安防”为主题，秉承“普及安防知识、展示先进技术、引领行业发展、服务市场需求”的办展理念，集产品展示、行业论坛、商贸洽谈、科技普及、技术推广等活动于一体，全面展示智能化安防技术与产品在平安中国、智慧城市建设中的创新发展与综合应用。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/07d146c7c208e311fc0f294d2317d28e.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2018北京安博会设立了国际馆、监控馆、智能楼宇馆、出入口控制与报警馆、智能交通与综合馆，以及公安技防综合应用馆，展览总面积约10万平方米，展位数量超过5000个，聚集了海内外1000多家企业，视频监控、智能家居、安防系统集成、智能交通、人工智能、无人机及人脸识别等多渠道、多领域的安防企业闪耀登场。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/65b90cc9e1bbf033c0449fcbd8b9ac55.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;广东前海秋叶原集团旗下深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司作为中国安防线缆著名企业应邀参展，本届展会秋叶原集团公司携“Choseal秋叶原”品牌7类万兆网线、光纤HDMI线、高品质AV影音线缆、智能工程线缆、强电线缆、多芯光缆、IT数码周边配套产品; 秋叶原商城WWW.91QYY.COM跨境电子商务平台; “蛇皇”高端新品牌产品等亮相安博会E3展馆F34展位。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/a6133b896775db5a966ac1dcb6d42e69.JPG\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">秋叶原智能工程线缆、强电线缆<br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/12d4e328168c9dcf66cb40035b491bff.JPG\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">秋叶原光纤HDMI线、高品质AV影音线缆</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/1b2c7b7e320429ddd73a8428f37889c4.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">秋叶原多芯光缆样品</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/377ed8dbea100febf43edc4bec8e5ed1.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">秋叶原旗下高端品牌—“蛇皇”，亮相安博盛会</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;秋叶原展位现场，人声鼎沸，热闹非凡，不仅有国内来自政府管理部门、行业用户、安防产品供应商、工程服务商、集成商、贸易商、零售商等多渠道、多领域的专业观众，还有不少国外厂商与采购商也聚集于此。或驻足观看产品，参加活动，或在展台里细细研看，秋叶原工作人员热忱地向观众介绍。</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/971b2471e6767d7bde2796976ad182f2.JPG\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/04d4eef33781cf99d22e88e405e614eb.JPG\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司成立于1989年，是一家集研发、制造和销售于一体的现代化企业，主营“Choseal秋叶原”牌高品质AV影音线缆、智能工程线缆、强电线缆、多芯光缆、电源转换器、IT数码周边配套产品，提供工程项目系统集成解决方案以及上下游原材料供应服务。<img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/ee376df21744bef164198f0bf9ef6212.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/a54350b35df86feb5dc95ad909e2c1a7.JPG\"/><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/028f5163b964b62c4e926b3617634790.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;秋叶原旗下工业园占地面积超20万平方米，先进设备达800余台次，生产人员规模过1000人，其中工程线缆日生产量达300万米。凭借优秀的品质和服务，秋叶原产品一直深受广大客户和消费者的青睐。“秋叶原”于2016、2017年荣膺广东省制造企业500强，是广东电线电缆行业10强企业，是广东著名商标及中国驰名商标，是电线电缆行业著名品牌。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/a23f866c7c8d6a3f5311df0b63e7af75.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2017年8月份，秋叶原成立了跨境电子商务商城平台， 致力于成为国际化的B2B+O2O智能连接产业互联网综合性平台以线上推广、线下展示、线上线下联动营销+服务支持为经营模式，向广大B端客户提供价格有优勢、质量有保障、服务更专业高效的行业全系列产品和配套解决方案。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">工程客户现场火爆订购秋叶原产品</span></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/fd9604537c9b02edf2303d293698961f.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/4068a7edbbd3f55a861994a658c6ef36.JPG\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/be8a5ded0a837bf33f9bdfc7d54cd013.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;当前，&nbsp;5G移动通信技术的标准制定正在如火如荼地进行中，随着大数据和万物互联时代的到来，新任务和新需求对移动通信网络发展提出了新的挑战，正推进着4G时代向5G时代的转化。当前正值新兴技术的工业革命时期，5G作为新一代的移动通信技术，将为万物互联和人工智能的发展提供良好的通信保障。<br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/b6b286675a7da55aa5c528f2f73deb80.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;与现有4G相比，用户数和用户需求的增加，导致网络密集化和业务多样化，同时5G还需要面对极致的性能要求，这些无疑对5G提出了极大的挑战，具体包括用户体验速率扩大10-100倍、更高的频谱利用率、毫秒级的端到端时延、大规模连接数扩大10-100倍、更低的应用成本以及良好的用户体验。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181101/a689a31ef24a9ef70dc5423cb173337c.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;面对5G时代的来临，秋叶原提出了“秋叶原5G网线，智领5G新时代”的发展口号，顺势而为研发出6A、7类万兆高速率网线以满足广大用户对5G万物互联新时代的需求！</span></p>', 5, 0, 1, 118, NULL, NULL, '2018-10-26 00:00:00', '2018-11-02 14:23:35', '/upload/image/20181101/381370f347abd9ec7505115a23edfb44.jpg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(97, 24, '英国安德鲁王子访问北京大学汇丰商学院，孙逸楷校董陪同热情接待。', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 0em; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">2018年11月1日上午，英国约克公爵安德鲁王子殿下到访北京大学汇丰商学院。英国驻华大使吴百纳女爵士、英</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 0em; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">国驻广州总领事梅凯伦女士等陪同来访。这是今年6月14日安德鲁王子访问北大汇丰英国校区之后，一年内第二次到访学院。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181102/523c3e5a69fb73f9b81e179085185c39.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">安德鲁王子与英国校区创始校董、</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">学院教师</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">交流、合影</span></strong><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">孙逸楷先生二排中间<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px;\">（</span></strong></span></strong>右6）</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>广东前海秋叶原集团孙逸楷董事长作为北京大学汇丰商学院英国校区创始校董成员对安德鲁王子的到访表示热烈欢迎，与北京大学汇丰商学院<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">教师</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">、</span></strong>英国校区创始校董们一行陪同安德鲁王子参观</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">校区。</span></span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></span></p><p><br/></p><section><section><img class=\" __bg_gif\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/49ZWuhWvBicJAUobrQvTavAEscK4USO89wHfNoQCib5U3fe5IsVHjWLib5qekv9rcDF0KKyEkt5bhXZ8vGda5icU7g/640?wx_fmt=gif&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 在</span>600余位学院师生的热烈掌声中，安德鲁王子来到B2报告厅，发表了主题演讲。他从 “龙门创将”（Pitch@Palace）的创立、使命和发展等维度出发，强调为优秀创业者提供全方位、强有力的创业支持及鼓励创新的重要性。“龙门创将”是由安德鲁王子于2014年发起的全球创新孵化平台，致力于汇聚各领域最具影响力的行业领袖，为创业者提供强有力的创业支持。目前平台已扶持了全球600多个创业项目，项目的成功率达95%。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181102/39c147c19c2d5c6b8af8aa8cc29850e4.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">安德鲁王子发表关于创新创业的主题演讲</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">安德鲁王子强调，各国的交流与对话非常重要，要通过教育加强对青年领袖创新能力和创业精神的培养。他将深入推进剑桥大学、北京大学等国际一流的中英高等学府在科研及学生培养方面的合作，为英国乃至欧洲的年轻人提供了解中国的契机，增进中英两国的交流。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\" __bg_gif\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/49ZWuhWvBicJAUobrQvTavAEscK4USO89wHfNoQCib5U3fe5IsVHjWLib5qekv9rcDF0KKyEkt5bhXZ8vGda5icU7g/640?wx_fmt=gif&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/></span></span></p><p><br/></p><section><section><section></section><section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 20px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>听完安德鲁王子热情洋溢的演讲，孙逸楷先生<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对其提出的看法</span>深表赞同，作为北京大学汇丰商学院英国校区创始校董，广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生持续关注高校各项教育事业及外交事务。在参加2018年1月13日校董会成立大会暨第一届校董会第一次会议时就已表示，北京大学汇丰商学院英国校区创建之初与广东前海秋叶原集团建立了校、政、行、企深度融合多边共赢的董事会办学体制，创建了紧密对接产业链的应用型人才培养体系，创新了与专业链对接的教学综合改革模式，实施综合改革，培养具有创意、创新和创业能力的“三创”人才，广东前海秋叶原集团愿与各方共建跨界融合平台，共享协同发展荣光。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181102/02481f46ad22675aa4dc451c952e045e.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 9px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;;\">广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生参加</span></span></strong><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 20px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 9px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;;\">北大英国校区校董会成立大会暨第一次会议</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181102/da45d328aebba98b3fa0bfd1924cc51d.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\