时代是一个资源整合、跨界融合的时代，更是一个开放合作、互惠共赢的时代。校企间的合作搭建起了教育链、人才链与产业链、创新链融合发展的全新平台，必将为企业转型发展注入新的强劲动力和提供有力的人才和智力支撑。秋叶原集团将始终秉持“开放包容、合作共赢”理念，围绕智能生活产业发展建设创新性、交叉性、实用性的行业特色和产业集群，全力推动人才培养供给侧和产业发展需求侧全方位融合，全力构建校企多方联动、产学研深度融合、资源平台共建共享协同发展新格局，愿全力持续深化合作、共赢未来。</span></p></section></section></section><section><section><section></section><section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181102/73e9ba0fb0ab2872ab151bd1a398ff72.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">安德鲁王子为新成立的“北京大学汇丰商学院未来媒体实验室”剪彩。</span></strong><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 13px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20181102/89a96030567cff648bc4eeccf9ce2d4d.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">最后</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">，安德鲁王子、吴百纳大使与海闻院长、陈玮教授共同为</span>“北京大学汇丰商学院创新创业中心” 揭牌。</span></p><p><br/></p>', 5, 0, 1, 118, NULL, NULL, '2018-11-02 11:59:33', '2018-11-02 12:00:05', '/upload/image/20181102/800de1f7397b863d07b37021cd560b85.jpg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN');
