(101, 25, '热烈祝贺秋叶原集团旗下供应链公司以过100亿营收规模荣膺2018年南山区经济突出贡献百强企业！', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190322/1b82c7de1fb049551dbaa3c4746c85ae.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">深圳南山区2018年度</span></strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">产值（营收）百亿以上企业荣誉奖牌</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190322/66e845a8a8b7e9c13e95037bfc01ad0e.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2019年2月25日（星期一）下午<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">，由中共南山区委员会、南山区人民政府主办的</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px;\">2018年度经济突出贡献企业TOP峰会在深圳人才公园求贤阁隆重举行，广东前海秋叶原集团旗下的秋叶原供应链有限公司、腾讯科技（深圳）有限公司、深圳今日头条科技有限公司、中兴通讯股份有限公司等标杆企业荣膺2018年南山区经济突出贡献百强企业。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190322/1715ee72f7fe0808178b629ccca915a5.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>在过去的一年里，南山持续高歌猛进，在工信部研究院赛迪顾问对全国</span>968个市（不含直辖市）辖区经济实力、增长潜力等17项指标综合评估中，南山区位居中国百强区之首。南山优质的营商环境，被《求是》杂志社中国小康网评为全国营商环境百强区（县）第三名，荣获社科院首届中国营商环境评估“创新引领奖”。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190322/78c2b03081992824814baf993b13ed46.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">南山</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">正一步步向世界级</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; 