(105, 24, '“连接未来 共赢天下” 热烈祝贺2019-2020秋叶原营销大会隆重召开！', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">2019年8月19-21日，2019-2020年深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司营销大会在美丽的东江之畔，毗邻秋叶原广东惠州产业园的博罗佳兆业万怡酒店隆重召开。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生携管理团队与来自全国各地的合作伙伴，以及与中国首家科学营销策划机构深圳市万讯智慧咨询有限公司专家团共襄盛会，面对市场环境的新变化，共同商讨“连接未来 共赢天下”的发展战略部署。</span></p><section><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/4312e880a2983f94a5a52da77852d7b1.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\"></span></section><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生为大会致辞</span></strong><br/></p><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 60px; font-size: 15px;\"></span></section><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\">会上，广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生发表了《连接未来 共赢天下》主题致辞，首先，孙董代表秋叶原集团公司董事会向应邀参加营销大会的各位嘉宾、合作伙伴、新老朋友们表示热烈欢迎和诚挚的问候！</span></p><section><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/fc3504f15064963f470e90a65f4848f2.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></section><p style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">广东前海秋叶原集团副董事长孙逸陈先生</span></strong><br/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\">孙董在致辞中强调，在5G、人工智能、智慧城市、智能家居、新零售时代来临之际，传统的线下销售模式正面临挑战，已难以适应未来市场竞争的需要，要改变发展策略，要加强线下线上融合一体化统筹兼顾协同发展部署，向新零售、新流量、新场景、新媒体、新价值、新营销思维模式转型。</span></p><section><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/1dd1ce00abce90f7b640fe2706969293.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></section><p style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 60px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">副董事长夫人张丽珠女士在本次大会上作感恩主题分享</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66);\"></span></strong><br/></p><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 60px; font-size: 15px;\"></span></section><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\">在品牌策略方面，围绕新零售发展部署，要转变以用户为中心，以市场为导向的运营思维，要统一品牌形象，以“品牌+用户+服务”模式驱动销售增长，并强调，地球是人类的家园，秋叶原品牌是秋叶原人的家园，号召大家一定要共同维护秋叶原品牌价值体系和形象。</span></p><section><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/196b632c450f36e2d5a9d2f7f5882c60.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 80px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"></span></section><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\">会上，公司市场、新零售、商城、电商、营销、工程、技术与制造各单位部门负责人分别做了2019-2020发展策略规划主题讲解，同时会上也邀请了优秀的合作伙伴代表分享宝贵的发展经验。</span><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/383f07d2f36db06309626d176643b55e.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司市场部总经理彭权宗先生作了《</span>2020年公司市场营销策略规划》主<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">题演讲，并详细阐述了公司未来将实施全新的战略部署，只要我们坚持以用户为中心，以市场为导向，以技术为支撑，共同维护秋叶原品牌价值体系，必将实现迎来更辉煌的发展。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></p><section><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/247ec15c9493b1877374d080f9b652bb.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/><br/></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\"></span></section><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司市场部总经理<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">彭权宗</span></strong>先生</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 37px; text-align: justify;\">深圳市前海秋叶原新零售科技公司总经理，深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司的副总经理孙梓超先生为我们主讲了《秋叶原新零售科技发展战略》，回顾了秋叶原30年的发展历程，面对新环境新时代，规划了新零售未来战略发展之路。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 37px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/2b3fbcf6b6dec136acf9bd526eb1d13b.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><section></section><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">深圳市前海秋叶原新零售科技公司总经理</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司的副总经理孙梓</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">超先生</span></strong></span></p><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\">秋叶原商城运营副总监刘萌女士《秋叶原商城研发与运营规划》介绍。</span></section><section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 37px; font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/9ec375ec3dee81016cda420c140a28b2.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 37px; font-size: 12px;\">秋叶原商城运营副总监刘萌女士</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\">深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司国内电商部赵亮经理代表电商部作了《顺风起航一电商零售》主题讲解。</span><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/07349aecbce412c18942ce34e6b9fee3.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司国内电商部经理赵亮先生</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\">深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司国内营销部总经理邹代斌先生作了《2018-2019年总结2020年度营销发展规划》讲解，回顾了多年来的营销历程，深刻分析了当前市场环境发生的本质变化，特别重点阐述了新的产品规划策略、价格体系策略和推广策略，为广大合作伙伴指明了新的发展之路。</span><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/82c07b776d45b0811199860f9445a250.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司国内营销部总经理邹代斌先生</span></strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司工程大客户部总经理孙利敬先生作了《工程大客户部销售政策》介绍</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px;\">。</span><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/7d88eaf1bd5fcdc306b6ffdddc41efe4.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\">深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司工程大客户部总经理孙利敬先生</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\">深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司技术研发总监兼线缆研究所所长王甫柱先生作了《新研发产品与综合布线前沿技术》分享。</span><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/38fb866deea718822a3cbbb5ea8da577.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司技术研发总监</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">兼线缆研究所所长王甫柱先生</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\">惠州市秋叶原实业有限公司总经理陈建法先生作了《惠州制造发展规划》介绍。</span><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/9ddc5d2201ea875da710693758223303.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 40px; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 40px; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">惠州市秋叶原实业有限公司总经理陈建法先生</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\">优秀合作伙伴代表重庆沐江科技有限公司总经理糜书洋先生以及北京市佳裕珩有限公司总经理刘睿良先生分别分享了《经销商如何利用好商城平台》与《工程开发经验案例分享》。</span><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/05adebc255742c7f940ab93552111c21.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">重庆沐江科技有限公司总经理糜书洋先生</span></strong></span><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/b51b2f040dc2f61461419855c8a2a78c.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">北京佳裕珩有限公司总经理刘睿良先生</span></strong></span></p><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></strong></span></section><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司综合管理部产品经理朱中良先生分别对公司推出的复合光纤</span>HDMI第二代产品、2.1版HDMI、5G系列、琥珀金系列、网络跳线等系统集成新产品作了现场推介，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">引起各位合作合作伙伴瞩目关注，现场人头涌动，大家纷纷踊跃咨询</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></p><section><br/></section><section><br/></section><section><section><section></section></section></section><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left;\">广东前海秋叶原集团&amp;</span></span></strong></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left; text-indent: 34px;\">深圳市万讯智慧咨询有限公司</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; text-indent: 34px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">战略合作签约仪式</span></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">大会次日，为推进集团公司品牌与营销策略升级，实施新零售发展部署，广东前海秋叶原集团与深圳市万讯智慧咨询有限公司隆重举行了《品牌营销咨询合作协议》战略合作签约仪式，将通过万讯智慧新型科学营销理念，品牌架构算法与大数据技术手段为秋叶原量身定制整体战略方案，加快推动秋叶原战略部署的落地实施，促进秋叶原在新的市场环境中焕发出新的强劲活力。</span></p><section><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/84723460395de07b11bb36550c208b4c.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></section><p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/41b7c0264b481af7def97be35eeccd88.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\">仪式结束后，中国首家科学营销策划机构深圳市万讯智慧咨询有限公司CEO魏华先生应邀作了《连接未来 共赢天下一经销商倍速盈利之道》主题演讲！魏总深刻分析了市场环境变化给秋叶原和各位合作伙伴带来的挑战，也介绍了面对新环境，各位经销商的科学营销增长之道，并对秋叶原未来的发展做全面的发展规划指导。</span></p><section><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/948089be3933b593affe62d0e87f1fb3.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></section><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(217, 33, 66);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 34px;\">深圳市万讯咨询有限公司CEO魏华先生</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\">大会最后，广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生作了总结发言，他指出，秋叶原专注线缆制造30+年，新时代营商环境的正在急剧变化，传统销售模式的危机越来越大，“物竞天择，适者生存，优胜劣汰”这是自然界的发展规律，拥抱时代，紧紧跟随公司的发展部署，不断加强学习互联网+新运营知识，组建商城电商运营团队，自我革新，与时俱进，才能跟上时代的步伐，只要我们携手同心，解放思想，继续开拓进取，终将取得改革发展的最后胜利。</span><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/upload/image/20190822/1d41b2769134406d109e48421b8263a3.JPG\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px;\">未来，公司将继续与广大合作伙伴一起，集思广益，共谋发展，共享秋叶原发展成果，连接未来 共赢天下。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', 5, 0, 1, 124, NULL, NULL, '2019-08-22 00:00:00', '2019-08-22 14:39:40', '/upload/image/20190822/063ecdc2118af7ac7d750ff6645bf925.jpg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN');
