ot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">HDMI</span>（High Definition Multimedia Interface）高清晰度多媒体接口，是一种数字化视频/音频接口技术。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">HDMI线</span>是多台高清晰度多媒体之间的连接线，能高品质地传输，未经压缩的高清视频和多声道音频数据。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200528/1590637615712386.jpg\" title=\"1590637615712386.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20200528113010.jpg\" width=\"359\" height=\"471\" style=\"width: 359px; height: 471px;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">由于它的使用范围广，所以奠定了其在消费类电子数字接口领域占有领先地位，在不同的应用领域有着完美的性能。所以在面对商家天花乱坠的宣传时，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">如何才能选择一条好的HDMI高清线呢？</span></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">第一步：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);\">问HDMI接口版本</span></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200528/1590637779906184.jpg\" title=\"1590637779906184.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20200528093115.jpg\" width=\"455\" height=\"231\" style=\"width: 455px; height: 231px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">4K/8K传输把很多行业都强制升级，HDMI标准也从1.4版本升级到2.1版本，在宽带和声音性能、画质都有了非常大的提升，并保持向下兼容，所以在购买HDMI线的时候，版本上注意购买最新的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.0/2.1</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">标准。</span></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">第二步：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);\">问HDMI接口型号</span></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">关于接口，HDMI协会共定义了下列五种：</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Type A&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">为市面上最常见的HDMI连接器种类，共设计有19pin，一般笔记型电脑、DVD播放器、电视、电脑萤幕等设备上都採用此种类。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Type B</span></strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">设计有29pin，频宽为Type A的两倍。理论上能够传输WQXGA（2560×1600）的高解析度，但是当时的HDMI 晶片无法运作在那麽高的时脉速度，所以市面上并没有产品採用。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro He