tion style=\"text-align: justify; max-inline-size: 100%; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“死较劲”的马自达，“创驰蓝天技术”就是它最好的答卷，这种永不妥协的挑战精神支撑着品牌独特的造车理念。对于音频线来说，秋叶原同样因为不服输不妥协，坚持为用户带来高品质的音改产品，务求让喜欢音乐的用户生活能变得熠熠生辉。</span></strong></span></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/><strong><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200713/1594608276365108.jpg\" title=\"1594608276365108.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp.jpg\"/></strong></span></p><p><br/></p><section style=\"text-align: justify; max-inline-size: 100%; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px 