/span></strong><strong><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"></span></strong></span></p><section style=\"text-align: justify; max-inline-size: 100%; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"></span></strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; transform: rotate(0deg); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></span></section></span></strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"></strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><p style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; transform: rotate(0deg); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">①3.5mm音频线：</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">这种音频线接头使用比较广泛，多用于电脑及便携式音源。例如笔记本、手机、MP3、DVD、电视机、收音机、电脑、CD机与功放机、音响之间的连接并传输它们的音频信号以及实现设备与设备之间对录，还可以适用于车载音频信号的传输。</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200713/1594608655948307.jpg\" title=\"1594608655948307.jpg\" alt=\"TB2IW6cw25TBuNjSspcXXbnGFXa_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">②6.5mm音频线：<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这种音频线适用于带有6.5mm的音频设备之间的信号连接，如功放，音响，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">吉他</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">，调音台等。</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200713/1594608672100396.jpg\" title=\"1594608672100396.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01ULF0eB1n0PVGd2biL_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em;\">③<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\">TRS线(莲花线)：这种音频线由于连接头部比较像莲花，故称“莲花线”，头部英文名称为RCA接头。用于带RCA复合视频信号接口的设备间的连接，如DVD、机顶盒等与电视间的连接；也可单独传输音频信号，如DVD机等音频设备连接到功放。</span></p><p style=\"font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200713/1594608767632047.jpg\" title=\"1594608767632047.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01Mh6D661n0PcJOFZCu_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\">秋叶原双莲花镀金音频线</span></p><p style=\"font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200713/1594608797708803.jpg\" title=\"1594608797708803.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01MUhmi91n0PWjxZfHM_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\">秋叶原三莲花镀金音视频线</span></p><p style=\"font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 2px;\">④XLR卡侬线：是一种平衡信号线，把它们插进插座时会有一声卡扣的咔嚓声，这样就避免了在不经意间把它们拔出来。卡侬线可以很长，且不会有杂音和信号干扰，<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">通常用于手持式麦克风和舞台使用的环绕声音响，广泛用于录音棚、舞台音响、视频影音系统工程。</span></span></p><p style=\"font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200713/1594608827724763.jpg\" title=\"1594608827724763.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01UallCJ1n0PVPJh7OO_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><br/></span></p><p></p><section data-autoskip=\"1\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;font-size: 14px;color: #ffffff;line-height: 1.75em;\"><section style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">这种音频线由于连接头部比较像莲花，故称“莲花线”，头部英文名称为RCA接头。用于带RCA复合视频信号接口的设备间的连接，如DVD、机顶盒等与电视间的连接；也可单独传输音频信号，如DVD机等音频设备连接到功放</span></strong></section></section><p></p></span></span></section><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">（二）数字信号音频线</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p><p></p><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">①数字光纤音频线：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">随着数字无损音源受到广泛应用，高品质光纤音源线备受重视。</span>它的物理接口分为两种类型，一种是标准方头，另一种是在便携设备上常</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">见的外观与3.5mm TRS接头类似的圆头。它是以光脉冲的形式来传输数字信号， <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">传输速度最快</span>，可以实现电气隔离，阻止数字噪音通过地线传输，有利于提高DAC的信噪比。</span></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200713/1594608923824436.jpg\" title=\"1594608923824436.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01eyLyqF1n0PWf95VzA_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">②MIDI（MIDI：乐器数字接口<span data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); transform: rotate(0deg);\">）：</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap;\">MIDI传输的不是声音信号，它传输的是数字信息（叫做事件信息），也就是信号开/关、音符、速率、拍子、音量等等。还有一种经常用作传输MIDI信息的USB线。</span></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200713/1594609010190494.jpg\" title=\"1594609010190494.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (1).jpg\"/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">当然啦，还有可通过不同类型的接头转换，实现更多不同设备的需求，比如：</span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200713/1594609132401175.jpg\" title=\"1594609132401175.jpg\" alt=\"6.5转卡侬公母话筒线麦克风线.jpg\"/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">6.5mm转卡侬音频线</span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200713/1594609050214943.jpg\" title=\"1594609050214943.jpg\" alt=\"3.5转三莲花音频线.jpg\"/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">3.5mm转三莲花音频线<br/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><br/></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">（三）音频线的特殊性</span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">一根好的音频线，应具有极低的传输损耗、良好的屏蔽性能，良好的接触性，而决定这些的最主要因素是：导线材料、绝缘材料、结构方式、插头和焊接方法，此外也与使用技巧有关。如：线的老化（即煲线）、连接方法、方向性等。</span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200713/1594609232227341.jpg\" title=\"1594609232227341.jpg\" alt=\"TB2YGXubBbM8KJjSZFFXXaynpXa_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">导体材料：既理想又经济的是无氧铜线，目前最常用的铜线纯度为99.99﹪(即4N)，<span style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\">用它制作的信号线，传输失真少、效率高、频响宽且均匀、动态强劲。</span>当然还有6N、7N、8N，甚至有9N的结晶铜。</span><br style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"/><br style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"/><span style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">绝缘材料：讯号线的外皮常用透明或不透明抗氧化PVC柔软塑料，内层绝缘用PE料更好，这样可以防止焊接时塑料的热熔、热缩现象。</span><br style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"/><br style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;outline: none 0px !important;\"/>结构方式：音频线<span style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text;\">结构通常是单根或两根芯线组成，线芯为多股铜线，每根线芯都较细；<span style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">有独立多层屏蔽（铝箔屏蔽、镀锡铜编制网、射频截至器）的双重同轴线、或二芯环绕结构的线，这两种结构的线，就可以将信号线的负极和接地线分开，不再公用,独立屏蔽，增强了抗干扰性。</span></span></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200713/1594609285825633.jpg\" title=\"1594609285825633.jpg\" alt=\"TB2aCBcaQfb_uJkSnhJXXbdDVXa_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">质好的音频线接头至关重要，要采用纯铜或专用合金材料，且表面镀金防氧化，顶级的还有卡环式的（带自锁的），焊点要牢且美观，以免振动松脱。从而可以保证与器材良好接触，减少信号的损失。<br/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></section><section style=\"color: rgb(255, 216, 2); font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">尽管音乐设备的广告总是天马行空，但是只有当你正确地用连接线把他们连接起来，他们才会发出美妙的声音，不是吗？</span></section><p></p>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2020-07-13 11:06:12', '2020-07-13 11:06:12', '2020-07-13 11:06:12', '2020-07-13 11:07:26', '/upload/image/20200713/5f0bc9e5e42ac.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN');
