Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\">不会被外力因素影响</span></strong></span></section><section style=\"white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; max-inline-size: 100%; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><br/></span></strong></span></section><p></p><p style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text;\">线缆主要由PVC塑料粒子加工护套绝缘以及各种规格的铜丝绞合成缆，根据用材按其结构的分布与功能，可分为</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>导体材料、绝缘材料、屏蔽材料、护层材料、填充材料</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text;\">等。</span></span><br/></p><p style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200715/1594780489267815.jpg\" title=\"1594780489267815.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (2).jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\">1.导体材料</span></strong></p><p style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\">导<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1.6px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(239, 244, 255);\">体</span>是线缆的主要组成部分<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">。</span>一般由<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 28px;\">铜、镀锡铜或铝制成<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1.6px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">大小是<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\">根据导体截面积来定义的</span>AWG<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1.6px;\">数</span>表示</span>，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1.6px; caret-color: red;\">导体截面积常用mm²或Cmil表示。</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: 1.6px; caret-color: red;\">而外加绝缘层、保护层的导线，则称为导电线芯。</span></span></p></section><p></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200715/1594780620947158.jpg\" title=\"1594780620947158.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (3).jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong>导<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(239, 244, 255);\">体</span>主要结构类型</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><section data-role=\"list\"><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;\"><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">单圆线：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\">主要品种有铜单线、铝单线等。</span>以导体直径<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\">为</span>结构参数，范围从0.01mm至3mm<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\">，除一部分作为产品直接使用外，</span>绝大部分是将单线绞制成多根绞线而使用的半成品；除单一材质的圆单线外，还有复合型圆单线，如镀锡铜等双金属圆单线。</span></p></li></ul></section><p></p><section data-role=\"list\" class=\"\"><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;\"><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">圆绞线：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">在生产、安装和使用中经受多次的卷绕和拉开，用较小直径的单线绞制成一定截面的绞线。根据不同的使用状况和条件要求绞制的线缆可不同程度的弯曲和扭曲。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200715/1594780714227934.jpg\" title=\"1594780714227934.jpg\" alt=\"镀锡铜，精炼铜1.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>设计原理：</strong></span></p></section><p></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><section style=\"line-height: 2em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">电源线一般依UL，IEC，JES，GB等相关标准设计</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">。（如：SVT、SJT、H05VV-F等）</span></span></section><section style=\"line-height: 2em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">电脑周边设备用线一般依UL，CSA等相关标准设计</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">。（如UL 1061、UL 2464、UL 2725等）</span></span></section><p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">特殊结构及特性标准</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">。</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">（如：USB 2.0，Serial ATA，IEEE 1284，IEEE1394，DVI，HDMI等）</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">通讯电缆一般采用铜材质作为导体，用以传输电流或电磁信号。</span></strong></span></p><section style=\"line-height: 2em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">（各线缆标准一般会规定导体尺寸，绝缘材质、厚度，外被材质、厚度，线材形状等参数。）</span></section></section><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2.绝缘材料</span></strong><br/></p></section><p></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">所谓绝缘就是包覆在导线四周隔绝电气的物质，既<span style=\"font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px;\">确保传输的电流或电磁波、光波只沿着导体行进而不流向外面，导体上具有的电位(即对周围物体形成的电位差、即电压)既能被隔绝，又保证导体的正常传输功能，和外界物体及人身的安全。</span></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200715/1594780854639822.jpg\" title=\"1594780854639822.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (4).jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">常用的<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.6px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">绝缘</span>材料有：<strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">PVC、PE、XLPE、氟塑料F、硅橡胶G</span></strong>等。<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">一般依线材电气特性及相应安规标准确定。</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p><p></p><section style=\"line-height: 2em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">一般线缆标准会规定绝缘最小平均厚度和任意点最小厚度。</span></section><section style=\"line-height: 2em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">（如：UL 1061规定绝缘材质为SR-PVC，最小平均厚度为9Mil（0.23mm）、任意点最小厚度为7Mil（0.18mm））</span></section><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br/></span>3.屏蔽材料</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.6px; font-family: arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">是一种将电缆产品中的电磁场与外界的电磁场进行隔离的构件，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">是一种“电磁隔离屏”</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.6px; text-align: justify;\">。除了能</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">置于产品的外部，还<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑;\">可</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">以<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">置于每一线对或多对数电缆的分组之间。</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200715/1594780908339447.jpg\" title=\"1594780908339447.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01mssGbW1n0PaaU8fEP_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p><section style=\"line-height: 2em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">依要求抗干扰的强弱，可采用单屏蔽和双屏蔽。</span></section><p></p><section style=\"line-height: 2em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">1）单屏蔽一般采用包铝箔屏蔽</span></strong></span></section><section style=\"line-height: 2em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">2）双屏蔽一般采用包铝箔后再加编织（或缠绕）屏蔽。</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></strong></span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"></span></strong></span></section><p></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><strong><span style=\"text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><strong><span style=\"text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">4.护层材料</span></strong><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">当线缆在各种不同的环境中安装运行时，必须具有对产品整体，特别是对绝缘层起保护作用的构件。包括：内衬层（内护套）、铠装层、外护套三部分。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200715/1594781200591268.jpg\" title=\"1594781200591268.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01gtYTcd1n0PbA26387_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">常用外被材质有<strong>PVC、PU、TPE、TPR<strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(239, 244, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">、</span></strong></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">铝、钢带</span></strong>等，<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1.6px; caret-color: red;\">一般依安规标准或客户要求而确定。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">5.填充材料</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">很多线缆产品是多芯的，有些绝缘线芯或先对绞成缆（或分组多次成缆）后，因为外形不圆整，或者绝缘线芯间留有很大空隙，所以在成缆时必须要加入填充结构。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200715/1594781650413058.jpg\" title=\"1594781650413058.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20200715105352.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">填充之后除了使成缆外径相对圆整利于包带、挤护套，也是为了使线缆结构稳定、内部结实，在使用时(制造和敷设中拉伸、压缩和弯曲时)受力均匀而不损坏电缆的内部结构。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200715/1594781834212888.jpg\" title=\"1594781834212888.jpg\" alt=\"1.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.6px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">主要材料:PP绳、麻绳、尼龙、棉纱</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">填充结构虽然是辅助结构，但也是必要的，其材料选用及形状设计上也有详细的规定。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: 