osoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">功率与音箱线的芯数是没有直接关系的，与音箱线导体的截面积和材质有直接的关系。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 2em; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">芯不能多，但也不能少。单芯线材力度是够了，但很冲、分离度不好。多芯的线材分离度够了，但力度不足。所以没有具体说要多少芯的，要看你对现在音箱的要求。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; transition: margin 0.1s linear 0s, padding 0.1s linear 0s, width 0.1s linear 0s, height 0.1s linear 0s; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 2em; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果你现在音箱觉得低频不够力，那么可以用少一点的芯，如果层次感、立体感不够，声音混在一起，那么就要用多芯的线，至于具体多少，需要自己慢慢调整。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200720/1595213965434529.jpg\" title=\"1595213965434529.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_202007161448311.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(93, 91, 91); overflow-w