-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">两百芯还是三百芯区别不大。如果接线距离比较远，要适当加粗音箱线，以免线上消耗的功率过于明显。</span></p></section><p><br/></p>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2020-07-20 11:05:12', '2020-07-20 11:05:12', '2020-07-20 11:05:12', '2020-07-20 11:09:50', '/upload/image/20200720/5f1509d7dd980.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN');
