(157, 24, '热烈欢迎博罗县领导一行莅临龙溪梦科园智谷信息产业园指导工作！', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\"><section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red; text-align: justify;\">2020年12月17日，博罗县县长谢远区携副县长周志亮，在博罗县龙溪街道办书记朱易彬，主任陈炳培，副主任高志芳等县、街道办领导陪同下，亲临</span><strong style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">龙溪梦科园智谷信息产业园</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red; text-align: justify;\">现场指导工作。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red; text-align: justify;\"><br/></span></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20201225/1608891321983213.jpg\" title=\"1608891321983213.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20201218155907.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><section style=\"white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #FF4C41;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 34px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">秋叶原集团<span style=\"text-align: left;\">孙逸楷</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: 34px; text-align: left; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">董事长在<span style=\"text-align: center;\">现场做</span></span></span></strong></span></section><section style=\"white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #FF4C41;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 34px; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">项目整体<strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">进度概述报告</span></strong></span></strong></span></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生以及副总裁庞云杰先生在现场为各级领导进行项目规划概况及总体建设进度作详细介绍，并针对项目遇到的政策困境以及一些实际困难展开讨论。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20201225/1608891333356279.jpg\" title=\"1608891333356279.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_202012181559071.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; text-indent: 0em;\"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; text-indent: 0em;\">考察中，博罗县领导班子一行为</span>解决企业的实际问题，在新兴产业园的设计规划等方面提出很多宝贵意见。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20201225/1608891361904815.jpg\" title=\"1608891361904815.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20201218145852.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><br/></p><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"101368\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto;text-align: center;\"><section style=\"display: flex;justify-content:center;align-items: center;\" hm_fix=\"410:186\"><section style=\"flex: 1 1 0%;background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(253, 123, 119, 0) 0%, rgb(233, 137, 143) 100%);height: 1px;margin-bottom: -5px;overflow: hidden;\"><br/></section><section data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; padding: 4px 1em; color: rgb(215, 46, 38); font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box;\" hm_fix=\"316:310\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">前沿阵地 谱写城市新篇</span></section><section style=\"flex: 1 1 0%;background-image: linear-gradient(to left, rgba(253, 123, 119, 0) 0%, rgb(233, 137, 143) 100%);height: 1px;overflow: hidden;\"><br/></section></section></section></section><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 104, 39); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">龙溪梦科园智谷信息产业园</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 104, 39); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">，是由广东前海秋叶原集团有限公司投资，旨在打造以信息产业为主导的国际工业4.0标准智能制造园区，是大湾区最具有人文情怀的田园山水式园区。为实现产城人文的有机融合，打造区域内的特色产业园区，引领周边产业转型升级和入园企业提供全方位的产业服务。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;\"><br/></p><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"101368\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto;text-align: center;\"><section style=\"display: flex;justify-content:center;align-items: center;\" hm_fix=\"410:186\"><section style=\"flex: 1 1 0%;background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(253, 123, 119, 0) 0%, #e9898f 100%);height: 1px;margin-bottom: -5px;overflow: hidden;\"><br/></section><section data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; padding: 4px 1em; color: rgb(215, 46, 38); font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box;\" hm_fix=\"316:310\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">前沿交通 对接融入大湾区</span></section><section style=\"flex: 1 1 0%;background-image: linear-gradient(to left, rgba(253, 123, 119, 0) 0%, #e9898f 100%);height: 1px;overflow: hidden;\"><br/></section><br/></section></section></section><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">项目总占地约</span><strong style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">10万平方米</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">，建筑面积超</span><strong style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">40万平方米</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">，地处大湾区东部深莞惠城市圈核心区位，龙溪高速公路入口处，与东莞桥头镇相邻，距离</span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">深圳中心区1.5小时</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">车程，是承接深圳、东莞产业转移的战略要地。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;\"><br/></p><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"101368\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto;text-align: center;\"><section style=\"display: flex;justify-content:center;align-items: center;\" hm_fix=\"410:186\"><section style=\"flex: 1 1 0%;background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(253, 123, 119, 0) 0%, #e9898f 100%);height: 1px;margin-bottom: -5px;overflow: hidden;\"><br/></section><section data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; padding: 4px 1em; color: rgb(215, 46, 38); font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box;\" hm_fix=\"316:310\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">前沿配套 荣享商务都汇</span></section><section style=\"flex: 1 1 0%;background-image: linear-gradient(to left, rgba(253, 123, 119, 0) 0%, #e9898f 100%);height: 1px;overflow: hidden;\"><br/></section><br/></section></section></section><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">同时项目靠近惠州龙溪环保电镀产业基地和太平山风景区，周边整体产业基础较好，活化优势、要素聚集、创新引领，紧抓大湾区产业转移及深莞惠一体化的发展机遇，充分发挥</span><span style=\"color: #FF4C41;font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">“3+2”</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">经济圈的纽带作用，精准打造“梦科园”在大湾区中的代表性IP。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">园区建成以后，为深圳等产业外溢企业以及电子信息产业上下游配套优质企业提供产业空间，形成产业集群，并且和全国规模较大的电镀基地形成产业园功能互补。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/