(164, 24, '《歌声献给党》热烈庆祝伟大的中国共产党成立100周年公益新春联欢会在深圳海雅大剧院精彩启幕！', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">热烈庆祝伟大的中国共产党建党100周年！</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 1.8px; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">1月15日</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">,</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">由中国西部研究与发展促进会和<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; text-align: start; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">一城一歌文化传播有限公司联合</span>主办，<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; text-align: start; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">深圳市宝安区音乐家协会</span>、拍歌（深圳）数字音乐科技有限公司承办，</span></span><span style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">广东前海秋叶原集团倾情协办的《歌声献给党》热烈庆祝伟大的中国共产党成立100周年公益新春联欢会在深圳海雅大剧院精彩启幕！</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">众多歌唱名家及舞蹈演员倾情献唱，热烈庆祝伟大的中国共产党建党100周年生日！本次晚会预计将在牛年春节期间由广东电视台与海南电视台等台隆重播出！</span></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></span></span></p><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30px;\">晚会</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; cursor: text; text-indent: 30px; letter-spacing: 1px; outline: none 0px !important;\">以歌唱党、歌唱祖国、歌唱家乡为主题。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em;\">将分为《腾飞吧中国》、《回顾往昔 &nbsp;砥砺前行》、《新时代接班人（少儿篇）</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em;\">》、《民族心&nbsp;&nbsp;中国梦》、《开拓创新 &nbsp;与时俱进》等五</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em;\">个篇</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em;\">章精彩演绎。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em;\">作为晚会的协办单位，广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生上台发表了致辞</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: left;\">：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !