vetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">俗称卡侬线，是一种平衡信号线，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">用于传输音响系统中（如均衡器、分频器、分配器或音箱控制器与功放之间）的各类音频信号。</span>它通过两个通道分别传送信号相同而相位相反的信号，接收端设备将这两组信号相减，干扰信号就被抵消了，就能获得高质量的模拟信号。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\">&nbsp;数字光纤音频线&nbsp;</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><br/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\">随着数字无损音源受到广泛应用，高品质光纤音源线备受重视。它的物理接口分为两种类型，一种是标准方头，另一种是在便携设备上常见的外观与3.5mm TRS接头类似的圆头。它是以光脉冲的形式来传输数字信号， 传输速度最快，可以实现电气隔离，阻止数字噪音通过地线传输，有利于提高DAC的信噪比。</span></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/></section></section><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"101848\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; line-height: 1.5em;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; display: flex;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; display: flex; align-items: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218); border-radius: 30px;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 4px 6px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(227, 108, 9); color: rgb(251, 213, 181);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">03</span></p></section><section data-brushtype=\"text\" hm_fix=\"240:401\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px 0px 15px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 16px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">HDMI高清线</span></p></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px 8px 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; width: 25px; flex-shrink: 0;\"><img data-ratio=\"0.8285714285714286\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/oJZWTpJpiae94jFnGpuXGLGfQ7Hu2T8cnXECselibyYL1W8Qdd10GtMQXc0TZcobjTia4IXnhfueX9ia4qK0c9Fe1w/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"35\" data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box; width: 19px; display: block;\"/></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210223/1614046194263105.jpg\" title=\"1614046194263105.jpg\" alt=\"HDMI.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 104, 39); overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">HDMI高清线可以同时传输视频与音频信号</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">，是一种数字多媒体接口，能高品质地传输未经压缩的高清视频和多声道音频数据。近几年上市的影音设备如4K蓝光播放机、智能投影仪、电视机等都将HDMI接口作为标配接口，所以在打造客厅家庭影院时视频线材中HDMI高清线是最重要的一根线一点也不夸张。</span></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">如果以后要接入智能家居系统，就还要给投影机预留一条网线，连接到智能中控机位置，方便以后传输232协议来控制。</span>低音炮，投影机需要预留电源，如果条件允许，尽量从总电箱单独拉4平方电源线过去，保证功率充沛，没有其他电器干扰。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">关于线材的选取还有很多的门道，线材作为家庭影院系统中重要的一环，在选择时一定要多比较，多看，经过合理搭配后才选择适合设备的线材。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">秋叶原</strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78); letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">历经30+年发展，各规格、场景使用的线材都是精工研发、制造的精品线缆，能满足各种消费环境所使用的各类型线缆，为消费者切实考虑<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; letter-spacing: 1px;\">，助力打造一个<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">完美的</span>家庭影院系统，即使错过了电影上映档期，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1px; outline: none 0px !important;\">在家也可以享受影院大片质感！</span></span></section></section>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-02-23 10:13:29', '2021-02-23 10:13:29', '2021-02-23 10:13:29', '2021-02-23 10:24:17', '/upload/image/20210223/6034646d43243.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(168, 24, '【科普】线缆应该如何存放', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"--tt-darkmode-bgcolor: #161616; --tt-darkmode-color: #F0282E; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">电线电缆产品种类众多，应用范围十分广泛，如果存放不当会影响线缆的寿命及使用安全，甚至造成不必要的灾害，所以如何存放就是一个需要重视的问题。</span></p><p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 248, 248); --tt-darkmode-bgcolor: #161616; --tt-darkmode-color: #F0282E; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 248, 248); --tt-darkmode-bgcolor: #161616; --tt-darkmode-color: #F0282E; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210301/1614565530248622.jpg\" title=\"1614565530248622.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp.jpg\"/></span></p><p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 248, 248); --tt-darkmode-bgcolor: #161616; --tt-darkmode-color: #F0282E; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">1.电线电缆存放要避免水源，同时酸、碱及矿物油类也不能接触，电线外皮多是塑料的,接触具有腐蚀性的液体会使电线外表皮发生溶胀，加速外皮损坏造成漏电，很危险。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">2.电线电缆不能长时间放在太阳底下暴晒或超高温的环境下，否则会导致线缆的外被出现裂痕或者起皮。<br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">3.储存电线电缆的环境中，严禁与有害线缆的气体存在，例如腐蚀性气体，易燃易爆炸气体。</span></p><p><br/></p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></span></div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">4.电线电缆存放要有规律，按规格以及</span><typo id=\"typo-380\" data-origin=\"出场\" ignoretag=\"true\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">出场</span></typo><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">时间进行存放，贮存期限以产品出厂期为限，一般不宜超过一年半。</span></p><p><br/></p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></span></div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">5.电线电缆长期存放会受到挤压力的影响，可能会导致护套及电缆变形，应定期滚动一次电缆，滚动后应检查电缆是否完好，避免有破损影响后续安全使用。（电缆盘不允许平放）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></span></div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">6.电线电缆的运输也是电线存放保护的关键，运输过程中严禁从高处扔电缆盘，这样很大的可能会导致绝缘、护套开裂，损伤线缆的导电性能和机械性能。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><div class=\"pgc-img\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></span></div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); --tt-darkmode-color: #FF0C00;\">救命小知识</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">如果电线电缆发生漏电起火，要立即切断电源，如果电气用具或插头仍在着火，千万不要用手去碰电器的开关；无法切断电源时，应该用干粉灭火器等专用灭火器灭火，不要用水或泡沫灭火器灭火。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210301/1614565570382864.png\" title=\"1614565570382864.png\" alt=\"图片6.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210301/1614565550241248.png\" title=\"1614565550241248.png\" alt=\"图片7.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">秋叶原始终坚持诚信为本、质量优先的原则，把用户的生命财产安全放在首位，凭借优良的产品、贴心的服务和良好的社会信誉，备受用户信赖，并不断把优质良心线缆产品奉献给广大消费者。</span></p>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-03-01 10:27:02', '2021-03-01 10:27:02', '2021-03-01 10:27:02', '2021-03-01 10:27:02', '/upload/image/20210301/603c50f0b9206.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN');
