 style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">4K超高清电视是一种分辨率更高的超高清电视，相比于全高清1920*1080，4K电视画面更清晰、细节更出众、动作更流畅、色彩更丰富、音效更真实。</span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(223, 228, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210415/1618478107134955.jpg\" title=\"1618478107134955.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN0192xPEJ1n0PgPB7LW0_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><br/></p></section><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"102512\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 4px; box-sizing: border-box;\" hm_fix=\"389:189\"><section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;width: 100%;height: 30px;background: rgb(158, 173, 248);margin-bottom: -34px;overflow: hidden;\" data-width=\"100%\"><br/></section><section style=\"display: inline-block;margin-left: 10px;\"><section data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; padding: 8px 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background: rgb(59, 92, 244);\"><p><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">4K电视需要满足什么标准</span></p></section></section></section></section></section><section><p style=\"text-align:center; color: rgb(16, 75, 197); white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><em><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 45px;\"><strong style=\"caret-color: red;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">01</span></strong></span></em></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center; color: rgb(16, 75, 197); white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"caret-color: red;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">配备专业级</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center; color: rgb(16, 75, 197); white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"caret-color: red;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">UHD超高清显示屏</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center; color: rgb(16, 75, 197); white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify; color: rgb(16, 75, 197); white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">4K超高清电视必须配备物理分辨率达到3840*2160(4K*2K)，像素达到829.44万的专业级UHD超高清显示屏，这和我们印象中熟知的1080P，也就是1920*1080有着天差地别。其显示屏屏体4K像素点排列紧密、分布均匀，显示图像更清晰，临场真实感也更强。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center; color: rgb(16, 75, 197); white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210415/1618478128921368.jpg\" title=\"1618478128921368.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01pT3UqH1n0PgMfld7q_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><br/></p></section><section><section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(16, 75, 197); line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><p style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><em><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 45px;\"><strong style=\"caret-color: red;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">02</span></strong></span></em></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"caret-color: red;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">4K解码芯片</span></strong><br/></span></p></section><p><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">4K电视必备的是4K解码，用户要观看到真正的4K视频，需要保证片源、传输和显示过程的4K画质，所以对电视处理器的要求更高，必须要配备专业的4K解码芯片<span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">以确保超高清信号从输入、解码、到显示的全通道超高清无衰减处理，真正实现超高清画面完整显像。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210415/1618478143721907.jpg\" title=\"1618478143721907.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01jGGYXN1n0PgQ2d9Lt_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p></section><section><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 45px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(16, 75, 197); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><em style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"caret-color: red;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">03</span></strong></em></strong></span></em></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(16, 75, 197); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\">具备USB3.0</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(16, 75, 197); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\">HDMI2.0及以上高速传输端口</strong></span></p></section><section><p><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">由于4K片源与普通片源相比有着巨大的信息量，这也对传输提出了新的要求。USB3.0、HDMI 2.0及以上版本可以更快速地传输4K信息源，保证了用户在观看4K电视时的流畅度，所以<span style=\"font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: start; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4K超高清电视至少应拥有一个</span>USB3.0、HDMI2.0及以上接口，才能支持真4K传输。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210415/1618478152191780.jpg\" title=\"1618478152191780.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01NCbCLD1n0PgJiGLgZ_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">当然，要实现4K超高清画质，高清连接线材是必不可少的。</span><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>秋叶原这款工程级HDMI2.0</strong></span><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">版高清线支持18Gbps传输宽带、4K<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\">@60Hz分辨率、</span>32声道音频以及HDR动态图像输出，让大屏高清更震撼，达到真4K高清全新视觉体验。</span></span></p></section><section><p style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><br/></p></section><section><section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(16, 75, 197); line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><p style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><em><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 45px;\"><strong>04</strong></span></em></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong>HDR高动态对比</strong></span></p></section></section><section><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">HDR高动态对比是大部分4K电视一个卖点，也是目前真4K标准之一。这个功能可以让画面的对比度更加强烈，直观的体验就是画面色彩更加丰富，并且完善了画面中的大部分细节，<span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: left; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial;\">带来更生动的画面效果。同时，</span>智能调节屏幕区域亮度，调节色域，展现更加丰富细腻的画面细节。</span></p></section><section><p><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210415/1618478172162767.jpg\" title=\"1618478172162767.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01KaBBoj1n0PdWKmmzs_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p></section><section><p><br/></p></section><section><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"102512\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding-top: 4px; box-sizing: border-box;\" hm_fix=\"389:189\"><section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;width: 100%;height: 30px;background: rgb(158, 173, 248);margin-bottom: -34px;overflow: hidden;\" data-width=\"100%\"><br/></section><section style=\"display: inline-block;margin-left: 10px;\"><section data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; padding: 8px 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background: rgb(59, 92, 244);\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">怎么辨别4K电视真假</span></p></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p></section><section style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: move; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; z-index: 0; letter-spacing: 0px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"><p style=\"text-align:center;max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;letter-spacing: 1.5px;outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; outline: none 0px !important;\">当你满心欢喜的买了一个4K电视机</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;letter-spacing: 1.5px;outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; outline: none 0px !important;\">发现呈现的画面并不如预想中的那么清晰</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;letter-spacing: 1.5px;outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; outline: none 0px !important;\">那你得考虑一下</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;letter-spacing: 1.5px;outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; outline: none 0px !important;\">买的4K电视机是不是真的啦~</span></p></section><section style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; cursor: move; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; z-index: 0; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"><section style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;outline: none 0px !important;\"><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210415/1618478221693867.gif\" title=\"1618478221693867.gif\" alt=\"640.gif\"/></p></section></section><section style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: move; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; z-index: 0; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(56, 55, 55); line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none 0px !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><p style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;outline: none 0px !important;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">大家可以看电视规格中的标识或者是外包装上是<strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">“R</span></strong><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">GB”</span></strong>还是</span><strong><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">“R</span></strong><strong><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">GBW”</span></strong><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">字样，如果是<strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">“R</span></strong><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">GBW”</span></strong>，那就是假的4K电视，因为4K电视采用的是</span><strong><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">“</span><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">RGB”</span></strong><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">模式<span style=\"font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\">。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210415/1618478232715658.jpg\" title=\"1618478232715658.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">另外还有一个简单的方法：用手机摄像头贴近电视屏幕，把焦距拉大拍一张照片。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210415/1618478239186012.png\" title=\"1618478239186012.png\" alt=\"640.png\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">放大照片后，如果我们可以看到红绿蓝（RGB）三个颜色依次排列，这就是真4K电视。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210415/1618478247686134.jpg\" title=\"1618478247686134.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (1).jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">如果发现除了红绿蓝三色外还多了白色（W),那么很有可能买了假的4K电视。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210415/1618478254953534.jpg\" title=\"1618478254953