iragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">展会由中国演艺设备技术协会主办，北京演艺展业广告有限公司与闻信展览联合承办。预计将带来1200家参展企业，展出面积近10万平方米，超50000名专业买家，峰会论坛及专场活动将超40场。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #ff4c00;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;caret-color: #ff0000;\">秋叶原</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: #e36c09;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;text-indent: 34px;caret-color: #ff0000;\">将</span><span style=\"text-indent: 34px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;caret-color: #ff0000;color: #000000;\">携音视频传输核心产品参展，引领音视频传输产品新潮流，</span></span><span style=\"color: #ff4c00;\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 34px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;caret-color: #ff0000;\">特向您发出展会邀请</span></strong></span><span style=\"text-indent: 34px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p><p><strong>展会信息：</strong></p><p><strong style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><br/></strong></p><p>展会时间：<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px;\">2021.4.14—4.16</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px;\">展会位置：</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot