(182, 24, '秋叶原成为首批入选城镇老旧小区改造创新推荐唯一弱电线缆品牌', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: left; text-indent: 34px;\">根据《中国建筑节能协会建筑节能与绿色建筑技术产品库及推广目录管理办法（试行）》要求，本着公开、公平、公正的原则，结合《关于开展“全国城镇老旧小区改造创新推荐产品、技术、项目”工作的通知》企业所申报资料，经专家评估论证，</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: left; text-indent: 34px; color: rgb(255, 76, 0);\"><strong>秋叶原成为首批入选城镇老旧小区改造创新推荐唯一弱电线缆品牌。</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><br/></p><section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210421/1618995611130933.jpg\" title=\"1618995611130933.jpg\" alt=\"1.webp.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210421/1618995547262825.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1618995547262825.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210421/1618995547829178.jpg\" title=\"1618995547829178.jpg\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14px;\">协会简介：</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: #666666;line-height: 24px;\">中国建筑节能协会是经国务院同意、民政部批准成立的国家一级协会，业务主管部门为住房和城乡建设部。协会由建筑节能与绿色建筑相关企事业单位、社会组织及个人自愿结成的全国性、 行业性、非营利性社团组织，主要从事建筑节能与绿色建筑领域的社团标准、认证标识、技术推广、国际合作、会展培训等服务。</span><br style=\"color: #333333;\"/><br style=\"color: #333333;\"/><span style=\"color: #666666;line-height: 24px;\">协会宗旨：落实党中央、国务院的决策部署，贯彻生态文明建设的总体方针，秉承“创新、协调、绿色、开放、共享”的发展理念，根据我国城乡建设发展和节能减排的战略目标，坚持以人 为本、依法推进，坚持节约资源和保护环境的基本国策，以打造“绿色、健康”建筑为己任，面向政府、行业、市场、企业、从业人员五个服务，大力推进建筑行业可持续发展。</span><br style=\"color: #333333;\"/><br style=\"color: #333333;\"/><span style=\"color: #666666;line-height: 24px;\">协会愿景：引领建筑向更高能效、更加健康的方向发展，营造未来可持续人居环境</span><br style=\"color: #333333;\"/><br style=\"color: #333333;\"/><span style=\"color: #666666;line-height: 24px;\">共同价值观：卓越 服务 创新 包容 合作</span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: #666666;line-height: 24px;\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: #666666;line-height: 24px;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210421/1618995635202506.jpg\" title=\"1618995635202506.jpg\" alt=\"src=http___p0.itc.cn_images03_20200601_5952b56aa567498695586119219c5706.jpeg&amp;refer=http___p0.itc.jpg\" style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14px;\">老旧小区的改造是党中央、国务院当前重点工作之一，我国已经从新城建设转向旧城更新时代。<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">随着&quot;新基建&quot;引领的新一轮科技革命和产业变革的深入，老旧小区迎来了功能转型升级的新机遇，<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">打造一个信息化、智能化的生活共同体成为老旧小区改造参与者和居民的共同追求。</span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><br/></span></span></span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210421/1618995688529359.jpg\" title=\"1618995688529359.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #FF4C00;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></strong></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #FF4C00;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">秋叶原作为<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">在智能连接领域的国家高新技术企业</span>，</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">此次成为首批入选城镇老旧小区改造创新唯一弱电线缆品牌，将用<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">5G<span style=\"text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">系列6A、7类、7A、八类网线、</span>8K超高清、低烟无卤等凝聚着<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">智慧和创新元素的高科技产品</span></span>，<span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: #FF0000;outline: none 0px !important;\">助力完善建筑功能、居住环境和社会基础服务设施，</span></span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 28px; widows: 1; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: none 0px !important;\">构建一个安全、稳定、高速的5G&nbsp;AI智慧小区，</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">让老旧小区彻底换“新颜&quot;</span>。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210421/1618995717282679.jpg\" title=\"1618995717282679.jpg\" alt=\"30.webp.jpg\"/></p></section></section></section>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-04-21 17:03:35', '2021-04-21 17:03:35', '2021-04-21 17:03:35', '2021-04-21 17:03:35', '/upload/image/20210421/607fea297d22f.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
