: rotateZ(-45deg);-ms-transform: rotateZ(-45deg);-o-transform: rotateZ(-45deg);\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">5</span></p></section></section><section style=\"margin-left:15px;color:#4b68fc;margin-right:15px;\"><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">多种场合轻松应对&nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">HDMI网线延长器其应用范围广泛，普遍用于一些需要HDMI信号调配和组合的领域。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210425/1619316010709056.jpg\" title=\"1619316010709056.jpg\" alt=\"9.webp.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">一般而言，需要高清影音远距离传输的设备都可以用到秋叶原HDMI网线延长器，如数字多媒体教学、家庭影院、视频会议、安防监控、电视广播、会展等带HDMI接口的设备上进行传输，让高清视觉始终如影相随。</span></p></section></section></section>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-04-25 10:02:34', '2021-04-25 10:02:34', '2021-04-25 10:02:34', '2021-04-26 10:34:38', '/upload/image/20210425/6084cd9ebda5b.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 