 justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">面向未来，秋叶原将继续坚持自主创新，培育技术新动能，孵化出更多新技术、新产品、新成果，<span style=\"font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\">以创新来驱动企业的发展和突破，塑造企业核心竞争力，<span style=\"font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">为</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\">业界提供源源不断的创新力量，</span></span>推动科技创新能力迈上新台阶。</span></section></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><section style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section></section></section>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-04-26 10:25:52', '2021-04-26 10:25:52', '2021-04-26 10:25:52', '2021-04-26 10:41:21', '/upload/image/20210426/608621ab28077.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN');
