(185, 24, '【干货科普】HDMI到底能不能热插拔', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p data-diagnose-id=\"29fa11ae68ccdc3dba813f0b20ca549d\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">HDMI作为当前最主流的视频接口，电视、电脑、笔记本等常见的电子设备中都配置了HDMI的接口。而在使用过程中HDMI接口能否热插拔存在诸多以讹传讹的谣言，给广大用户在使用时造成了很大的困扰。到底HDMI接口能够热插拔吗？</p><p data-diagnose-id=\"77faa8b1b997a18d9b66236ec91c4498\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">什么是热插拔</span></p><p data-diagnose-id=\"77faa8b1b997a18d9b66236ec91c4498\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210510/1620612731644895.jpg\" title=\"1620612731644895.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01qusUsC1n0PfzRwDzA_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></p><p data-diagnose-id=\"cd66312f53e446b988d48d212f095215\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><br/></span></p><p data-diagnose-id=\"cd66312f53e446b988d48d212f095215\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">热插拔就是带电插拔，</span>此功能允许用户在不关闭系统、不关闭电源的情况下取出和更换硬件，从而提高了系统对灾难的及时恢复能力、扩展性和灵活性等。热插拔技术是实现电源连续运行和不停机维护的关键技术。<br/></p><p data-diagnose-id=\"0ab707fae2a47972b3224cee5632d268\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">平时我们接触到热插拔最多的接口就是USB，外部设备在不关闭系统的情况下就可以随意拔插，也不会造成损坏，大大增强了便捷性。</p><p data-diagnose-id=\"e13ea4cc5da4801c4a6ad1444acf5048\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">HDMI接口理论上也是支持热插拔的</span>，这也是HDMI区别于VGA、DVI未设计螺丝、卡扣等固定装置从而方便接驳外部设备，便于用户拔插的原因。<br/></p><p data-diagnose-id=\"d4fbe6378a4f3ac73d72f8c38baf6ede\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">HDMI热插拔原理</span></p><p data-bjh-caption-id=\"cap-79451823\" data-diagnose-id=\"baff7f892bb29b6861ac662db7ce889b\" class=\"bjh-image-container cant-justify\" data-bjh-helper-id=\"1620612211222\" data-bjh-caption-text=\"请点击输入图片描述（最多18字）\" data-bjh-caption-length=\"16\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: relative; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><div contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"bjh-image-helper bjh-clear-at-out-put\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 300px; bottom: 0px; pointer-events: none; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-end; transform: translateX(-50%); margin-left: -192px; width: 384px;\"><span class=\"bjh-image-func-delete\" title=\"删除图片\" style=\"display: block; position: absolute; top: -10px; right: -8px; width: 17px; height: 17px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgb(178, 178, 178); cursor: pointer; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; transform: scaleX(1);\"></span><div class=\"bjh-image-func-wrapper\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; height: 21px; display: flex;\"><span class=\"bjh-image-func-crop\" style=\"display: inline-block; height: 21px; width: 64px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; pointer-events: auto; user-select: none; margin-right: 24px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); border-radius: 2px; font-size: 12px;\">编辑</span><span class=\"bjh-image-func-search\" style=\"display: inline-block; height: 21px; width: 64px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); border-radius: 2px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; pointer-events: auto; user-select: none;\">搜图</span></div></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210510/1620612757251493.jpg\" title=\"1620612757251493.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20210428141639.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">HDMI标准里面的有一个管脚的名字就叫</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; font-weight: 700;\">Hotplug</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">，HDMI线插到设备上（比如电视）后，Hotplug引脚会被拉高，发送信号端检测到这个高电平信号后才会发送HDMI信号。</span></p><p data-bjh-caption-id=\"cap-67822926\" data-diagnose-id=\"446144c52755f86220d7368286027aeb\" class=\"bjh-image-container cant-justify\" data-bjh-helper-id=\"1620612211223\" data-bjh-caption-text=\"请点击输入图片描述（最多18字）\" data-bjh-caption-length=\"16\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: relative; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><div contenteditable=\"false\" class=\"bjh-image-helper bjh-clear-at-out-put\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 300px; bottom: 0px; pointer-events: none; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-end; transform: translateX(-50%); margin-left: -192px; width: 384px;\"><span class=\"bjh-image-func-delete\" title=\"删除图片\" style=\"display: block; position: absolute; top: -10px; right: -8px; width: 17px; height: 17px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgb(178, 178, 178); cursor: pointer; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; transform: scaleX(1);\"></span><div class=\"bjh-image-func-wrapper\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; height: 21px; display: flex;\"><span class=\"bjh-image-func-crop\" style=\"display: inline-block; height: 21px; width: 64px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 21px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; pointer-events: auto; user-select: none; margin-right: 24px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); border-radius: 2px; font-size: 12px;\">编辑</span><span class=\"bjh-image-func-search\" style=\"display: inline-block; height: 21px; width: 64px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); border-radius: 2px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; line-height: 21px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; pointer-events: auto; user-select: none;\">搜图</span></div></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210510/1620612781355856.jpg\" title=\"1620612781355856.jpg\" alt=\"398685027.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p data-diagnose-id=\"4d49996b01b6b2493f9157f1aaf1d867\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">迄今为止，HDMI从1.0历经多个版本的演变发展到HDMI2.1，其实从第一个版本开始就支持热插拔。另外，常用的HDMI-A、HDMI-C、HDMI-D也都支持热插拔。<br/></p><p data-diagnose-id=\"b4ba2b38a3bbf92ed78c83bbe486812e\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">为何HDMI热插拔会损坏设备</span></p><p data-diagnose-id=\"6cb771c82b87e91b1b6bfb8c61a8e45a\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">HDMI在理论上支持热插拔，那为什么生活中还是有不少在热插拔的时候损坏了接口甚至是电器的案例呢？</p><p data-diagnose-id=\"6cb771c82b87e91b1b6bfb8c61a8e45a\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210510/1620612814103195.jpg\" title=\"1620612814103195.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01O6XZaO1n0PX28EZEu_!!398685027.jpg\" style=\"color: rgb(152, 152, 152); font-family: PingFangSC-Regular; font-size: 14px; text-align: left;\"/></p><p data-diagnose-id=\"2f5a016910fc9851948f2e223a342b1b\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p data-diagnose-id=\"2f5a016910fc9851948f2e223a342b1b\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">HDMI传输高速数字信号，为了支持较高的传输速度，发送与接收芯片中采用的抗静电保护电路，仅能承受5-8KV静电电压。</p><p data-diagnose-id=\"b350e556aa9704c7c255a44906012f55\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">在实际环境中，干燥的空气等因素，都会为静电电压产生提供有利条件，高质量的源端和显示端设计中，往往会选择牺牲部分电容余量而配置ESD保护电路，但部分电子设备为了节省成本，会将ESD保护电路省去，那么产生静电的HDMI插入后，就会烧毁芯片。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p data-diagnose-id=\"2a7ecc6fa1c1c8a290aa2c8fdc054177\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">虽然目前大部分设备的HDMI接口都有防静电设计，部分HDMI高清线也具备静电保护，热插拔产生的静电不会造成损坏。<br/></p><p data-diagnose-id=\"bdf314b441fc17517470e5ecb497efe2\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">但是一些山寨劣质产品因为成本的问题可能不会有防静电设计，所以才会产生热插拔损坏设备的情况发生；或者HDMI线材绝缘性可能做<span class=\"strategy_error_words\" data-bjh-target=\"得\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"color: red;\">的</span>不够好，出现短路的情况也是有可能的，另外接头没有进行电镀处理，就很容易生锈造成接口物理损坏。</p><p data-diagnose-id=\"bdf314b441fc17517470e5ecb497efe2\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210510/1620612829995080.jpg\" title=\"1620612829995080.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01xDXRhC1n0PbPczBlV_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p><p data-diagnose-id=\"f842443f9fdf72338072bc4deb8bca27\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">所以，选择HDMI线时要认准<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">高品质HDMI高清线</span>，接口镀金有更好的防腐蚀、导电性和耐高温能力，还有防静电设计，热插拔产生的静电不会接口造成损害。</p><p data-diagnose-id=\"b6da4e6d17c3524175bd4f957f54bd02\" style=\"margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">但是再好的线也有爱惜的必要，长期高频率的热插拔或多或少都会造成损害，如果大家在使用时发现HDMI接口不够用，也不用急着频繁插拔更换，我们可以选择<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">多进一出的HDMI切换器</span>，多个画面自由切换，操作实施方便，也不会损坏HDMI线。</p>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-05-10 10:16:14', '2021-05-10 10:16:14', '2021-05-10 10:14:46', '2021-05-10 10:16:14', '/upload/image/20210510/609896fd5f681.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
