(189, 24, '【揭秘】HDMI分配器、切换器、网线延长器该怎么选！', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\"><section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\"><section><section><section><section><section style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align:justify; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">HDMI是当前主流视频接口，大家在会议工程、监控项目和日常生活中肯定看到或接触过</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>HDMI分配器、切换器、网线延长器、转换线</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">等让人眼花缭乱、长相神似的HDMI周边器材。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">它们究竟有哪些用途？适用于什么样的应用场景，该怎么选呢？</span></p></section></section><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top: 15px;margin-bottom: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">1.HDMI分配器</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top: 15px;margin-bottom: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 15px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: #FF4C41;\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210604/1622774294173873.jpg\" title=\"1622774294173873.jpg\" alt=\"分配器.jpg\"/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom: 15px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: #FF4C41;\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom: 15px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: #FF4C41;\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">HDMI分配器</span></strong></span><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">是多端口输出的设备，可以将输入的HDMI信号分配成多路一致、同步的HDMI信号输出。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom: 15px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">经常在<span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;caret-color: #FF0000;line-height: 21px;outline: none 0px !important;\">培训、监控指挥中心、零售、卖场展示、远程视频会议等这些<span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">需要</span>经常用多个显示设备显示同一个画面的场合中使用。<span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">通常有1进4出、1进8出等HDMI分配器。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-top: 15px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">秋叶原HDMI分配器</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">支持4K*2K/30Hz分辨率，</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">内置双智能芯片，即插即用、观影顺畅、传输不失真；采用喷漆外壳、镀金接口，抗干扰、不易生锈，增强信号传输的稳定性，确保传输画质不受损；配备5V1A电源，提供强劲动力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">2.HDMI切换器</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 15px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"color: #FF4C41;\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210604/1622774314980891.jpg\" title=\"1622774314980891.jpg\" alt=\"切换器1.jpg\"/></span></strong></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"color: #FF4C41;\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></strong></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"color: #FF4C41;\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">HDMI切换器</span></strong></span><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">是将一路或多路HDMI信号分别传输给一个或者多个显示设备，如两台电脑主机要共用一个显示器,矩阵切换器可以将两台电脑主机上的内容任意切换到同一个或多个显示器上。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">切换器在一些演出或是高清视频会议系统、</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text;\">商场广告宣传、医疗系统等</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">需要频繁切换视频信号源，而手动切换信号不仅花费时间，还极容易出错、导致严重现场事故的场合早已广泛<span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">应用</span>。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-top: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">而随着家庭娱乐设备的与日俱增，越来越多的视频终端需要接入电视，诸如安卓盒子、PS4、电脑等等，但电视机的HDMI接口往往只有一到两个，面对众多外设输入设备，电视上的HDMI接口会变得捉衿见肘了，拔来插去的，实属麻烦。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-top: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"caret-color: red; line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">秋叶原HDMI切换器</span></strong></span><span style=\"caret-color: red;line-height: 150%;\">完美解决家庭生活中输入设备过多而电视机HDMI接口匮乏的痛点，<span style=\"caret-color: red;line-height: 150%;\">兼容Windows、iOS、安卓等各种主流系统，无需安装驱动，即插即用；<span style=\"caret-color: red;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;\">支持4K/60Hz超高分辨率；配置红外遥控/按键双重选择，</span></span></span><span style=\"caret-color: #FF0000;\">一键顺畅切换</span><span style=\"text-align: left;caret-color: red;\">。</span></span></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">3.HDMI网线延长器</span></strong></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: red; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); outline: none 0px !important; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210604/1622774357184468.jpg\" title=\"1622774357184468.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01Y0YvEU1n0Pc1pM9YE_!!398685027 (1).jpg\"/></strong></span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: red; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); outline: none 0px !important; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: red; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); outline: none 0px !important; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>HDMI网线延长器</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: red; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; outline: none 0px !important;\">是<span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;caret-color: red;\">用来延长信号的器件，</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px;\">由一个发送器与一个接收器所组成，中间可使用Cat6/Cat6A网线连接延伸，<span style=\"caret-color: red;\">确保信号长距离无衰减传输，</span></span><span style=\"caret-color: red;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在成本上与HDMI线材对比价格更低，是长距离传输中经济实惠之选。且容错成本低，整条传输线路中单独一个配件损坏都可以更新替换使用。</span></span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">秋叶原HDMI网线延长器</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: red;\">单网线延长可达150米</span></strong></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，真正打破了距离的限制，享受1920*1080高清画质。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 28px;\">一般而言，高清影音设备需要远距离传输都可以用秋叶原HDMI网线延长器。</span></span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 28px;\"><br/></span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">4.HDMI高清转换线</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210604/1622774392858637.jpg\" title=\"1622774392858637.jpg\" alt=\"HDMI转DVI7.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 1.8px; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 1.8px; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">当你的输入设备和输出中同时都设有DVI接口和HDMI接口时，直接使用HDMI/DVI线缆连接线的效果是最好的，但如果存在一端</span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 1.8px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">只<span style=\"background-color: #FEFFFF;\">有HDMI接口，但另一端只有DVI接口时，就可以用两种接口的转换线材在设备之间进行连接。</span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 15px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(57, 57, 57); outline: none 0px !important; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">如</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); outline: none 0px !important; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>秋叶原HDMI转DVI</strong><strong>高清线</strong></span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(57, 57, 57); outline: none 0px !important; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">双线转换，一线多用，支持1080P</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;color: #393939;outline: none 0px !important;\">高清画质，让画面栩栩如生</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 15px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">当然，还有其他转换线，比如HDMI转VGA、<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\">Type-C</span>转<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\">HD</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\">MI</span>等等<span style=\"color: rgb(57, 57, 57); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; outline: none 0px !important;\">，</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">摆脱接口的限制</span>。</span></p></section><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 15px;margin-bottom: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 25, 25); text-align: left; line-height: 150%; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">生活中多视频设备同时使用、切换使用、远距离使用或需转换使用已经成为常态，为了解决这些问题，HDMI相关的周边器材肯定会经常涉及，大家只需要了解它们的区别，根据自己的实际需求选择相对应的器材即可！</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-06-04 10:42:37', '2021-06-04 10:42:37', '2021-06-04 10:42:37', '2021-06-04 11:06:18', '/upload/image/20210604/60b9930e5828e.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
