(191, 24, '【新品速递】秋叶原蓝光系列光纤DVI高清连接线完美解决远距离传输问题', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\"><section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><section style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; widows: 1; text-align: justify;\">DVI是继VGA之后的又一个接口形式，即数字视频接口，是一种高速传输数字信号的技术，它可以进行高质量的数字信号传输。和过去的VGA信号相比，DVI信号有很大的优点，比如：传输速度快、消除拖尾、信号无衰减、画面清晰等等。</span></section></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.5em;\"><p style=\"widows: 1; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p></section><section style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.5em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210618/1624000026396223.jpg\" title=\"1624000026396223.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp.jpg\"/></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; text-align: start; text-indent: 34px; widows: 1; caret-color: red; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\">DVI线缆有单通道与双通道两种传输模式，<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">但有一个很大的缺点，就是传输距离短。</span></span></span></span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; text-align: start; text-indent: 34px; widows: 1; caret-color: red; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><p style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"><br/></p></span></span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; text-align: start; text-indent: 34px; widows: 1; caret-color: red; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"></span>市面应用较多的是双通道的型号，因长距离传输技术未能得到实质性突破，这个缺点极大地限制了DVI设备的普及和应用。目前最远传输距离依然为30米。一旦超过了最远距离，就会出现严重的传输速度慢，拖尾，衰减以及画面模糊等现象。<span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"></span></span></span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; text-align: start; text-indent: 34px; widows: 1; caret-color: red; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"></span></span></span></section><section style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section><section style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.5em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210618/1624000001825512.jpg\" title=\"1624000001825512.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20210617174001.jpg\"/></section><section style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; widows: 1; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span></section><section style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section><section style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; widows: 1; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">而工程上又经常会碰到需要将高清音视频信号传递到30米以上乃至上百米距离的项目，很多工程的设计、施工人员经常会为既要传输高清信号、又要解决超长距离传输音视频信号的问题而劳心劳力，备受困扰。</span></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><section style=\"line-height: 1.5em;text-align: center;\"></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><section style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; widows: 1; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">因此，如何延长DVI信号的传输长度又保证信号能实现高清传输就成为了一个迫在眉睫的问题。</span></section><section style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><p style=\"font-size: 14px; widows: 1; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p></section><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210618/1623999990166986.jpg\" title=\"1623999990166986.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_202106181046314.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"104160\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto;\"><section style=\"font-size: 53px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: rgb(0, 176, 240);margin-left: 10px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>01</strong></span></section><section style=\"margin-top: -30px;transform: rotate(0deg);transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-ms-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);\"><section style=\"background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218); padding-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">秋叶原<strong style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: left; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\">光纤</span></strong>DVI高清连接线化解行业难题</span></strong></span></section></section></section></section></section><section data