(196, 24, '【科普】线材对传输音频信号有什么影响', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" class=\"\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\" class=\"\"></section><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">在音响系统中，除了讲究功放、音箱、音源等设备外，传输音频信号的连接线材也颇为讲究。因为</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; caret-color: red; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">音频信号的传输是在线材里面来执行的，线材决定<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">了</span>音频信号传输的稳定性，<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">而</span>音频信号的稳定影响着音乐的品质。</span></span></section><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; text-align: center;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210716/1626404670332639.jpg\" title=\"1626404670332639.jpg\" alt=\"027.jpg\"/></span></section></section><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">1.</strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; caret-color: red;\">线材对传输音频信号有什么影响</span></span></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">对线材关注的重点，是让音频信号在传输过程中没有改变，即零失真。但在实际使用中，线材存在着电阻、电容、电感等会对通过的音频信号产生影响，使得信号在传输中形成欠阻尼、漏失音乐信息和细节模糊等现象。</span></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\" class=\"\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\" class=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/></section><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\">由于存在电容和电感，所以传输电缆就具有其特殊的频率特性，即对不同频率的信号有不同的时延（也即所谓不同的传输速率）和呈现不同的阻抗，显然，这会使信号产生一定的失真。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\">音乐信号并非像电力一样只有50或60hz，在流动的过程中同时含有各种频率成分的变化，不但要承受大能量，而且还要做到能无损失的传送复杂的音乐讯号才行。</span></p><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span styl