404705462624.jpg\" title=\"1626404705462624.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">1)<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">精炼铜真&quot;芯&quot;打造</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); caret-color: red; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"></span></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">一条好的线材应该具备低电容、低电感、低电阻与低集肤效应等物理性。铜是应用最广泛导体材料，拥有超高的导电率、高延展性、抗撕裂性，可以保证电信号和音频信号高效传输，最大程度的避免音染和失真现象，保持声音的高还原度。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p></section><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">另外，高纯度无极性的PVC、PE及特别定制的填充棉等这些高级材料都是保证线材良好特性的基础。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210716/1626404716355526.jpg\" title=\"1626404716355526.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01IRmf9P1n0Pa5CPp1w_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\" class=\"\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px;  letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 0.5px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">2)接触性良好，多次插拔后的耐用性好</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 0.5px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"></span></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2.2px;  line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">线材接头接触性不佳，线芯断裂，则容易造成声音或图像信号劣质化甚至断讯，这绝不是消费者所能接受的。而我们在使用各种影音器材时，不免会因保养、变更摆放位置、换机等不同原因，将线材多次拆下和插上，一条质优的线材绝不能因经过多次的插拔后出现接触不良的现象。</span></p><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px;  letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2.2px;  line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"></section><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2.2px; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210716/1626404728267302.jpg\" title=\"1626404728267302.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01sgbn0K1n0PVtMQffS_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2.2px;  line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px;  letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">3)极低的传输损耗、良好的屏蔽性能</span></strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2.2px;  line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgba(90, 90, 90, 0.84); font-size: 14px;  letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">线材的主要目的是传输信号，所追求的终极目标应是将信号真实完整无缺地传输，不因线材本身材质和结构造成信号损耗或出现失真引致声染色。故好的线材本身的阻抗和容抗要与器材间形成良好的匹配，<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">使信号得以百分百的传送。</span>另外，<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">线材本身良好的防辐射屏蔽隔离效果，可以</span>避免受到外在电磁和射频干扰，使信号得以无损传输，<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">干扰到正常的音频和视频信号，产生信噪比劣化现象</span>。</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 2px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"></span></span></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><br/></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\" class=\"\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">要知道“线”在整个音响系统中，应该是一个忠实的传递者。而好的线材与差的线材两者之间不仅选用的材料不同，内部的结构原理也不尽相同，所以无论是信号传输性能还是抗外来电磁干扰的性能都有一定差别。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, 微软雅黑, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">所以一定选择靠谱的品牌，买靠谱的线！</span></span></section></section></section></section></section></section></section>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-07-16 11:12:10', '2021-07-16 11:12:10', '2021-07-16 11:12:10', '2021-07-16 11:12:10', '/upload/image/20210716/60f0f7a690b50.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(197, 24, '【分析】VGA接口会被被淘汰吗', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">目前，我们比较常用的视频接口有VGA、DVI、HDMI</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">、DP</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">，其中</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">应用最广的</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">是HDMI，就有人觉得而作为元老级接口的VGA的市场占有率越来越低，是接口界的xp，ie6，office2003，是钉子户应该被淘汰，其实不然。</span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210720/1626744586790653.gif\" title=\"1626744586790653.gif\" alt=\"640.gif\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">VGA(Video Graphics Array)<span style=\"text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">，也被称为D-Sub接口,</span>是IBM于1987年提出的一个使用模拟信号的电脑显示标准。VGA接口即电脑采用VGA标准输出数据的专用接口。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">VGA接口共有15针，分成3排，每排5个孔，显卡上应用最为广泛的接口类型，绝大多数显卡都带有此种接口。它传输红、绿、蓝模拟信号以及同步信号(水平和垂直信号)，从块头巨大的CRT显示器时代开始，VGA接口就被使用，并且一直沿用至今。</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">它本身还有其他接口没办法替代的亮点，因此并没有退出市场。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210720/1626744601568363.jpg\" title=\"1626744601568363.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01EpPeDU1n0PVatuE4b_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">首先大部分与视频相关的旧设备都匹配有VGA接口</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">，比如投影仪、显示器等，其特点就是</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">不容易损坏、</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">使用寿命长，如果VGA淘汰了，那就意味着老设备要换新，对企业来说成本很大，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: red; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">所以对应的VGA接口也得以保留更久。</span></span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">其次VGA接口素来价廉物美，安全可靠，性能也不错</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">。HDMI因为有专利以及制造问题，成本并不低，同等长度的价格要比VGA高近一半。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">千万别觉得只有HDMI接口才能进行高清信号的传输，VGA同样可以显示1080P的图像，<span style=\"caret-color: red; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">所以用它连接显示设备观看高清视频是没有问题的</span>。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; text-indent: 28px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">而且虽然它是种模拟接口，但是由于VGA将视频信号分解为R、G、B三原色和HV行场信号进行传输，所以在传输中的损耗还是相当小的。外加VGA的兼容性很好，不会像HDMI那样发生不同版本的接口不兼容的现象。所以这种又便宜，又好用的设备，当然不容易被淘汰咯。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210720/1626744623843200.jpg\" title=\"1626744623843200.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01yWjFlJ1n0PVatwEpV_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">最后为了保护接口，在挪动和碰撞中起到固定作用，防止闪屏现象的发生，延长<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">使用寿命，</span></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">VGA接口处都采用机械螺丝固定</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">，这点很实用哦!</span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><section data-support=\"96编辑器\" data-style-id=\"24974\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"_135editor\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">虽然你不一定用过HDMI或DP接口的设备，但你肯定用过VGA的，所以，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\">目前市场上对VGA接口的需求并不少，它也不会那么轻易就被被淘汰。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">如果你有需要就上秋叶原各大官方平台购和线下专营店购买一条属于你的高品质VGA连接线</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">吧。</span></span></span></p></section></section>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-07-20 09:32:02', '2021-07-20 09:32:02', '2021-07-20 09:32:02', '2021-07-20 09:32:02', '/upload/image/20210720/60f62773c16ce.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN');
