stify;\">获评南山区<strong style=\"text-align: center; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify;\">2021-2023年度</span></strong>“绿色通道”企业</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify;\">荣誉称号，<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">为公司带来了一系列辖区内的优惠政策以及便捷服务。</span></span></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"text-align:left;max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: left; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">据悉，南山区从1998年起，在全区范围内开展评选“绿色通道”企业活动，并对获选企业颁发“绿色通行证”，使持证企业享受到更优惠的政策和更便捷的服务。“绿色通道”评定企业范围覆盖南山区纳税百强、工业百强、上市企业、独角兽企业等。</span></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210812/1628761441621165.png\" title=\"1628761441621165.png\" alt=\"2.png\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210812/1628761495753413.png\" title=\"1628761495753413.png\" alt=\"640.png\"/></p></section><p style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(241, 92, 25); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">”绿色通道“企业可享受服务政策（截取部分）</span><span style=\"caret-color: red; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(241, 92, 25); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">此荣誉的获得，<span style=\"font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(54, 54, 54); letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, sans-serif;\">代表南山区政府对公司价值和贡献的支持与认可，</span></span>意味着公司可享受南山区包括人才扶持措施、纳税服务、知识产权保护、人才健康管理等111条服务措施，在出入境、户政、申报认定等涉及政府审批事项上，可享受“直通车”式的便利审批与跟踪协助，<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; caret-color: red; color: rgb(54, 54, 54); letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为企业提供精准式服务。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210812/1628761515794662.jpg\" title=\"1628761515794662.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">未来，<span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: left; white-space: pre-wrap;\">在政府部门的保驾护航下，</span>在政策利好、行业向上的大环境下，秋叶原将继续保持<span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, sans-serif;\">行业领先的创效能力，<span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">在全球科技革命和产业变革中稳步高质量发展，继续发挥优秀企业的示范带动作用。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"caret-color: red;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210812/1628761527675606.jpg\" title=\"1628761527675606.jpg\" alt=\"4.jpg\"/></p></section><section style=\"margin-right: 0%; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0%; box-sizing: border-box; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"caret-color: red; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p><font color=\"#3f3f3f\" face=\"Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><b>关于公司：</b></span></font></p><p><strong><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">深圳市前海秋叶原新材料科技有限公司</span></strong><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">成立于2015年9月，是</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">广东前海秋叶原集团</span><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">的全资子公司之一。主营业务大宗商品有色金属铜杆，电解铜，铝锭，锌锭，锌合金，铝棒，电解镍，铅锭现货批发贸易和期货的套期保值，同时还为客户提供包括订单代采，货物质押，仓储物流等业务。</span></p></section></section>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-08-12 17:47:01', '2021-08-12 17:47:01', '2021-08-12 17:47:01', '2021-08-12 17:47:01', '/upload/image/20210812/6114ee125c48c.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN');
INSERT INTO `news` (`id`, `news_cate_id`, `title`, `short_title`, `content`, `admin_id`, `count`, `is_show`, `sort`, `start_time`, `end_time`, `create_at`, `update_at`, `pic`, `pics`, `seo_title`, `seo_keyword`, `seo_description`, `platform`, `lang`) VALUES
(206, 24, '【科普】网络从1G到5G的演进历程', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">从20世纪80年代发展至今，移动通信技术由</span>1G的大哥大→2G王者诺基亚→3G CDMA→4G LTE→5G万物互联，<span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">经历了五代的变迁，每一代移动通信技术的发展都带来了时代的变迁，我们的生活也因此变得便捷丰富。</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210817/1629167053568609.jpeg\" title=\"1629167053568609.jpeg\" alt=\"0d2b99cdb0d9424c9aa58f95f40b1acd.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">这是一段怎样的通信旅程呢？</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1G：模拟语音时代</span></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p><br/></p></section><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1G是第一代移动通信技术，<span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\">制定于上世纪80年代，<span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">它是</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\">以模拟技术为基础的蜂窝无线电话系统，如今已淘汰的模拟移动网，</span></span>在无线通信历史上，它坐上了第一把交椅。<span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\">1G无线系统在设计上只能传输语音流量，并受到</span>网络容量<span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\">的限制。</span>AMPS<span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\">为1G网络的典型代表。</span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p></section><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">1G时代 “最贵的仔<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\">（售价贵、通讯贵）</span>”——</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\"><strong>大哥大</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">，它只能进行语音传输，接打电话，<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 32px;\">还</span>有距离的限制<span style=\"text-indent: 32px;\">，容易出现串号、盗号的现象，不久就被淘汰了</span>，如今，只能成为很多人的回忆了。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210817/1629167086731466.jpg\" title=\"1629167086731466.jpg\" alt=\"src=http___ztd00.photos.bdimg.com_ztd_w=700;q=50_sign=a01d923cfad3572c66e29edcba28121a_ca1349540923dd54fc8262bdd909b3de9d824876.jpg&amp;refer=http___ztd00.photos.bdimg.jpg\" style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong>2G：数字语音时代</strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; zoom: 1; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2G是第二代手机通信技术规格，<span style=\"text-indent: 34px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">一改模拟通信方式，</span>以数字语音传输技术为核心，开启了数字通信之路。<span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\">相较于第一代移动通信技术，第二代移动通信具备高度的保密性，系统的容量也大幅增加，同时比1G多了数据传输服务，手机从这一代开始可以上网了，最早的文字简讯也从此开始。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; zoom: 1; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2G时代也是移动通信标准争夺的开始，由欧洲起家的GSM（Global System for Mobile Communication）脱颖而出，成为最广泛采用的移动通信制式。伴随着GSM的崛起，在欧洲起家的诺基亚和爱立信开始攻占全球市场，仅仅用了十年，诺基亚就成了全球最大的移动电话商。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; zoom: 1; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; zoom: 1; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 0em; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong>3G：CMDA大行其道的时代</strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; zoom: 1; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">3G是第三代移动通信技术</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px;\">，是指将无线通信与国际互联网等多媒体通信结合的新一代移动通信系统。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 32px;\">2009年1月7日，中国发了三张3G牌照，分别是中国移动的TD-SCDMA，中国联通的W-CDMA和中国电信的WCDMA2000，中国进入了3G时代。</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 32px;\">在3G 之下，我们有了更高频宽和稳定的传输，视频电话和大量数据传送更为普遍，移动通讯也有着更为多样化的应用。</span>由于无线通信和互联网的结合，智能手机和平板电脑得以迅猛发展，3G更是被视为是开启移动通讯新纪元的关键。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong>4G：移动互联网新高度</strong></span></p><p></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\">4G是第四代</span>移动通信技术<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">，是<span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">2013 年才开始正式挺进人们视线里的小鲜肉<span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\">，</span></span>能够传输高质量视频图像，以及高质量图像。进入4G时代后，全球移动通信标准呈现出进一步融合的趋势。从影响力上来看，4G可以说是专门为移动互联网设计的通信技术，不论是从网速、容量和稳定性上来看，4G相较于上一代3G技术都有了明显的提升，</span><span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\">并能够满足几乎所有用户对于无线服务的要求。</span></span></p></section><p></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">4G网络通信速度的极大提高，高清图像和视频等数据得以快速传输，<span style=\"text-indent: 32px;\">移动互联网开启了一股新的浪潮，移动支付、滴滴、美团等新兴产业和应用的发展繁荣兴盛。</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210817/1629167105879049.jpg\" title=\"1629167105879049.jpg\" alt=\"0e2442a7d933c895dd287f63dd1373f082020057.jpg\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong>5G：万物互联的时代</strong></span></p><p><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\">5G是第五代</span>移动通信技术<span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\">，5G 网络主要有三大特点：</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">高速率，</span></strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">不仅仅是3秒钟下载1部超高清电影这么简单，VR、AR、云技术将与生活无缝对接；</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">高可靠低时延，</span></strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(191, 54, 12); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">毫秒级</strong>通信时延,让无人驾驶、远程手术不再遥远；</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">超大数量终端网络，&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">达到<strong style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(191, 54, 12); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">百万/平方公里</strong>&nbsp;的联网终端,将形成更广阔和开放的物联网，让智慧家居、智慧城市成为可能。</span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">信息随心至，万物触手及<strong style=\"font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; max-width: 100%; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(191, 54, 12); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">，</strong></span></strong><span style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">在5G网络中，数据传输速率是惊人的，速率稳定维持在2Gbps以上， 也就是250MB/s。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210817/1629167124582655.jpg\" title=\"1629167124582655.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01kX6nFF1n0Pi2WgOO0_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">为了匹配5G网络，需要新建和升级改造大量的5G基站和高速宽带环境的数据中心，需要数量巨大的高速通信网线。</span>因此对拥有万兆高速传输能力，满足5G时代高速率、大容量、低延时<span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-indent: 32px;\">的</span><span style=\"text-indent: 32px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\"><strong>秋叶原</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-indent: 32px;\">七类（CAT7）、超七类、四万兆八类（CAT8）网线的需求迎来了大爆发。</span></span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210817/1629167139780058.jpg\" title=\"1629167139780058.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20210303155316.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 32px; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\">同时也需要对家用网线进行更新换代，</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">具有</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">10Gbps传输速率，<span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: left;\">500MHZ带宽的秋</span></span><strong><span style=\"text-align: left; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">叶原<span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\">超六类（CAT6A）网线，</span></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">成为<span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 34px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: left;\">家庭和企业办公5G万兆高速传输的<span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">首推<span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 34px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: left;\">入门</span></span>网线。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 34px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: left; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">历史的车轮是在泥泞中前进的，不是在高速路上前进的。<strong style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: inherit; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(191, 54, 12); box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></strong>从1G到5G，主要区别在于速率、业务类型、传输时延，以及各种移动通讯等采用了不同的技术，遵循不同的通讯协议，<span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify;\">经历了</span></span><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: left; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">萌芽<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">、</span>成长<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">、</span>修正<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">、</span>提升<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: left; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: justify;\">一系列过程，</span>所以，让我们继续期待新未来吧！</span></span></p></section><p></p>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-08-17 10:30:03', '2021-08-17 10:30:03', '2021-08-17 10:30:03', '2021-08-17 10:32:59', '/upload/image/20210817/611b1f2541e2a.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(207, 24, '正义力量！秋叶原与市场监督管理局联手严惩商标侵权行为', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\"><section data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\"><section class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 0em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">近日，重庆市九龙坡市场监管局在辖区查获一起假冒“秋叶原”商标侵权案。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">九龙坡市场监管局执法人员在渝州五金机电城内<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\">发现</span>售卖的网络线缆产品<span style=\"max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-indent: 34px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在包装和实物上标注有“秋精叶品原”、“秋香叶港原”等字眼，且有意将“秋叶原”字体突出放大，误导消费者误认其“<span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">产品</span>”系我司“深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司”产品，强行与“秋叶原”品牌产生联系，使相关公众产生误认，利用“秋叶原”合法注册商标蒙骗消费者，<span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">对秋叶原品牌形象及经销网络造成损害，</span>扰乱市场秩序！</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><section style=\"opacity: 0.35;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"135编辑器\" class=\"_135editor\"></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: red;max-width: 100%;text-indent: 34px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Choseal秋叶原作为线缆行业30+年的耕耘者，</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-indent: 2em;caret-color: red;\">始终认为坚守品牌自主及变革创新是企业和产品成功的根本，公司从创立之日起，在科研创新方面投入未曾停歇，努力钻研。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-indent: 2em;caret-color: red;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210820/1629454338450865.jpg\" title=\"1629454338450865.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20210303155316.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">先后成立“秋叶原电线电缆研究所”、“秋叶原电线电缆实验室”、2018年与国家副部级单位 — “</span><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 34px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">中国兵工学会</span><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red; text-indent: 34px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">”合作成立“中国兵工学会军工安防研究院深圳分院”，为国家安防事业发展做出行业领域贡献，紧跟5G、8K等时代技术发展潮流，在万兆传输领域、8K音视频传输领域、接插件领域都取得卓越贡献。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red; text-indent: 34px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; caret-color: red; text-align: justify;\">并获得“中国驰名商标”、“国家级高新技术企业”、“中国电线电缆百强企业”、“国家电线电缆手册修订组专家成员”等多项代表着研发实力的殊荣。</span><br/></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: red;text-indent: 34px;\"><br/></p><p><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">品牌的美誉势必会招来市场上一些别有用心商家的觊觎，秋叶原对待这些商家也始终保持</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>零容忍</strong></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">的态度！自商标注册以来，秋叶原从未间断商标维权工作，以维护自身的合法权益。</span><br/></p></section><section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"135编辑器\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: center;isolation: isolate;margin: -10px 0% 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;flex: 0 0 0%;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;line-height: 1;\"><section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"135编辑器\"><section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;display: inline-block;width: 15px;height: 15px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;background-color: #ffffff;\"><section><svg viewbox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\" xml:space=\"default\"></svg></section></section></section></section></section></section><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"105519\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 10px auto;\"><section style=\"font-size: 28px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: #cf1512;line-height: 40px;text-shadow: 1px 1px 0px #f8ae04;\" hm_fix=\"344:734\"><span style=\