if;\">执法人员现场对经营者进行宣传教育，要求涉嫌侵权的商品立即停止销售，将涉嫌侵权的商品进行没收、封存，并告知经营者等候调查处理，同时提供相关来源及授权证明等材料。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important; text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important; text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210820/1629454294238991.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1629454294238991.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210820/1629454294227723.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1629454294227723.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210820/1629454294386424.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1629454294386424.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important; text-align: center;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">维护秋叶原品牌的市场声誉始终是我们对客户的严肃承诺，秋叶原将进一步加大维权力度，切实维护“秋叶原”商标的合法权益。<span style=\"caret-color: red;\">如果大家发现有类似的假冒、仿冒、未经授权侵犯秋叶原品牌和字号的行为，请积极、主动、及时地与当地<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\">市场监管局</span>或秋叶原公司法务部门联系。让我们携手合作，共同监督，维护良好的市场环境。</span></span></p></section></section></section></section