(208, 24, '【分析】如何选购水晶头', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: red; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">在综合布线中，网线是传输环节的一个重要产品，常见的有超5类、6类、7类、8类之分，与之对应的水晶头也有超5类、6类、7类、8类之分。<br/></span></p><p><br/></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210903/1630635861612094.jpg\" title=\"1630635861612094.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01wBd8tM1n0PeEWSfKH_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">如果水晶头搭配不当，即使其他网络布线产品应用的很好，也可能会产生电磁干扰导致网速卡顿，甚至</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; outline: none 0px !important;\">整个链路都瘫痪。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; outline: none 0px !important;\"><br/></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">那么，应该怎么选择水晶头呢？</span></strong></span></p><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"93743\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"text-align: center;\"><section style=\"width:6em;display: inline-block;\"></section></section></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 76, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;1.看网线类别&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 76, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></strong></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">水晶头类别和网线类别相匹配即可，如超五类网线用超五类水晶头，六类网线用六类水晶头，七类网线选七类专用带燕尾夹的屏蔽水晶头<span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210903/1630635875767361.jpg\" title=\"1630635875767361.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01yko23V1n0PeE00FAl_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 76, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.看屏蔽类型&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 76, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></strong></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">非屏蔽网线选非屏蔽水晶头即可，如果是屏蔽网线就选屏蔽水晶头（包括一些列配套器材都需要选屏蔽的，如网络面板、模块等），才会达到最佳屏蔽效果。</span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210903/1630635888686414.jpg\" title=\"1630635888686414.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01KEkw0k1n0PeEh6GZU_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">目前市场上水晶头是多种多样的，很多不负责任的商家，为了获得销量，用降低产品质量、低价销售的方式，这样就导致他们采用回收料或者工业等级很低的材料作为水晶头的原材料进行生产，这些产品不仅性能达不到使用要求，同时还极大的污染环境。</span></p></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong>那什么样的水晶头才是高品质的呢？</strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong>1.标识：</strong>优质的水晶头在塑料弹片上都有厂商的标注;</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong>2.芯片：</strong>这是最关键的一点，优质的水晶头上芯片会采用镀金工艺，颜色纯正光亮，比较粗厚，可以降低链路传输损耗，保证传输的稳定性；</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong>3.可塑性：</strong>用线钳压制时可塑性差的水晶头会发生碎裂等现象;</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong>4.弹片弹性：</strong>质量好的水晶头用手指拨动弹片会听到铮铮的声音，将弹片向前拨动到90度，弹片也不会折断，而且会恢复原状并且弹性不会改变!将做好的水晶头插入集线设备或者网卡中的时候能听到清脆的&quot;咔&quot;的响声;</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong>5.透明度：</strong>好的水晶头是晶莹透亮的，就跟它的名字一样，边角光滑无瑕疵。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; zoom: 1; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">大家可以按照这些小技巧去选购水晶头哦~</span></section><section style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 15px; zoom: 1; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210903/1630635912219762.jpg\" title=\"1630635912219762.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01HMAwxB1n0PVMmJsLV_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; zoom: 1; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">虽说在网络传输产品中，水晶头可以说是最小的设备之一，但它却起着非常大的作用，在选购时切不可大意，也不可贪图小便宜，最终酿成大祸。</span></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">其实想要找到好的水晶头也不难，</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-align: left; outline: none 0px !important;\">可登陆</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-align: left; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); outline: none 0px !important;\">秋叶原</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-align: left; outline: none 0px !important;\">各大官方商城或线下授权体验店购买：水晶头<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 28px;\">种类齐全，选用的材质均为优质PVC料制作，</span>晶莹透亮，镀金芯片传输更稳定。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-09-03 10:53:23', '2021-09-03 10:53:23', '2021-09-03 10:53:23', '2021-09-03 10:55:24', '/upload/image/20210903/613187af919ee.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN');
INSERT INTO `news` (`id`, `news_cate_id`, `title`, `short_title`, `content`, `admin_id`, `count`, `is_show`, `sort`, `start_time`, `end_time`, `create_at`, `update_at`, `pic`, `pics`, `seo_title`, `seo_keyword`, `seo_description`, `platform`, `lang`) VALUES
(209, 24, '【科普】HDMI线有方向性分正反吗', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\"><section style=\"white-space: normal;\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\"><section style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\"><section style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\" class=\"\"></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"text-align: left; caret-color: red;\">自HDMI标准诞生以来，以其出色的性能实现了音频视频讯号的高效传输，</span><span style=\"text-align: left; caret-color: red; text-indent: 28px;\">广泛应用于机顶盒、DVD播放机、个人计算机、电视、游戏主机、综合扩大机、数字音响与电视机等设备，势头如日中天。</span></span></p></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: none 0px !important;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: none 0px !important;\">常用的HDMI高清线分为</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 76, 65); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: none 0px !important;\">普通HDMI线和光纤HDMI线</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: none 0px !important;\">两种，因两端都是一模一样的接头，让不少用户发出疑惑：HDMI线在使用时有方向性吗？有正反之分吗？</span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span style=\"caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">普通HDMI线</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; outline: none 0px !important;\">普通HDMI线也就是铜缆HDMI线，传输距离在</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; letter-spacing: 1px; background-color: rgb(255, 76, 65); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: none 0px !important;\">30米以内的</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; outline: none 0px !important;\">是目前最为普及的HDMI产品，不论是日常游戏、办公、打造家庭影院还是在工程应用中都是很常见的。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; outline: none 0px !important;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; outline: none 0px !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210906/1630894234410478.jpg\" title=\"1630894234410478.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01NqvaIW1n0PgSDAOAs_!!398685027.jpg\"/></span></span></p></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">铜缆HDMI传输的是纯弱电信号，输入端到输出端的传输信号都是直接互通不需要调解，</span>所以</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 76, 65); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: none 0px !important;\">没有方向性不分正反</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: none 0px !important;\">。线缆的两端可以任意连接<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">输入端</span>或<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">输出端</span>，均不会对传输信号效果产生影响。</span></span></p></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 15px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong>注意</strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">要实现铜缆HDMI信号远距离传输，厂家为保证较长距离信号的强度和稳定性，会在接口处添加信号放大器，这种加有信号放大器的长米数铜缆HDMI线就需要分正反方向（如有的产品标注<strong style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">TV</strong>端的必须连接电视等显示设备），在使用时要注意线身的标志。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210906/1630894292798878.jpg\" title=\"1630894292798878.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20210805164225.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom: 15px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span style=\"caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify; margin-bottom: 15px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span style=\"caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">光纤HDMI线</span></strong></p><section style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; outline: none 0px !important;\">HDMI线传输载体不断变化，以光纤作为载体的HDMI高清线火了起来，<span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: none 0px !important;\">它和铜缆HDMI的传输特性不同，</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: none 0px !important;\">中间线身部分为光纤传输介质，需要通过两次光电转换才能实现信号传输。</span><br/></span></p></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; outline: 0px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; outline: 0px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\" class=\"\"><br/></section><section style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><section style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red; outline-style: initial;\">首先需先将信号源端发射出来的电信号经过输入端调制芯片转化为高速光信号，由光信号经过中间的光纤部分耦合传递至信号输出端；</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red;\">再由输出端经过光电转换调制芯片,将光信号调解成播放端可识别的数字电信号，才算完成整个视听信号传输的完整过程。</span></span></p></section></section><section style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></section><section style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><section style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: 0px;\">两次光电转换的过程不可逆，因此光纤HDMI线使用时是</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 76, 65); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有方向性区分正反的</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;\">，</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red;\">必须正确对应连接插口。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red;\"><br/></span></span></span></p></section></section><section><section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"></p></section></section><section style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><section style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: 0px;\">标记着</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 76, 65); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;\">“</span><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;\">SOURCE</span></strong><span style=\"outline: 0px;\">”为信号输入端</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;\">，</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red;\">插在电脑主机、DVD等设备上；</span></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red;\"><br/></span></span></span></p></section></section><section style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 0em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><section style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: 0px;\">标记着</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 76, 65); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;\">“</span><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;\">DISPLAY</span></strong><span style=\"outline: 0px;\">”为信号输出端</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: 0px;\">，插在电视等各种高清显示设备上即可。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: 0px;\"><br/></span></span></p></section></section><section class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align:center; line-height: 1.75em;\"></p></section><section style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\" class=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210906/1630894327409402.jpg\" title=\"1630894327409402.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_202108051642253.jpg\"/></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">HDMI光纤线堪称长距离传输的未来。</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; background-color: rgb(255, 76, 65); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">秋叶原第三代复合光纤HDMI高清线，</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: start;\">150米超长光电智慧</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">，领衔新标杆，不受外部电磁干扰，<span style=\"caret-color: red;\">信号传输衰减几乎为零，不需要担心传输带宽问题，可以尽情的享受音质效果和绚丽多彩的高清画面。</span></span></span></p></section></section></section></section></section>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-09-06 10:13:05', '2021-09-06 10:13:05', '2021-09-06 10:13:05', '2021-09-06 10:13:05', '/upload/image/20210906/6135791e6a9d0.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
