inkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p><section data-id=\"98767\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"margin:10px auto;\"><section style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/UH19PdPjIicsKWpSlR7rOV0o28ZeD5xBkBB2zg6aJYicBoRUCxGaiaelibP6BpqNnq797KZDTuVCCwicahkc5B0ib81A/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot;);background-size: cover;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: center top;padding: 3px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"background-color: #ffffff;padding: 1em;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;font-size: 14px;\"><section data-autoskip=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><section data-role=\"title\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"106349\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 10px auto;\"><section style=\"display:flex;align-items: center;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block;margin-right: 10px;\"><section style=\"background-color: #f84541;padding: 5px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>集团公司</strong></span></section></section></section><section style=\"flex: 1;\"><section data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: #f84541;text-align: left;margin-left: 5px;\"><br/></section><section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;width: 100%;height: 1px;background-color: #f96a67;margin-top: 3px;overflow: hidden;\" data-width=\"100%\"><br/></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">广东前海秋叶原集团是一家以线缆生态链、产业园投资运营与互联网+布局，集研发、生产、销售及园区运营服务于一体的<span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">国家级高新技术企业集团，</span