nt-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify; outline: 0px; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211101/1635732464667441.jpg\" title=\"1635732464667441.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20211029155118.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify; outline: 0px; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify; outline: 0px; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">在新的历史时期，秋叶原将<span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; letter-spacing: 0.533333px; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;;\">继续秉承</span><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px; letter-spacing: 0.533333px; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;;\">“以科技和服务创造美好生活”的企业使命，</span>不断开拓创新，锐意进取，进一步提升核心竞争力，勇当科技排头兵，积极投身于粤港澳大湾区建设和深圳先行示范区建设的热潮中，为推进深圳经济发展作出更大贡献。</span></p></section></section></section>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-11-01 10:08:55', '2021-11-01 10:08:55', '2021-11-01 10:08:55', '2021-11-01 10:08:55', '/upload/image/20211101/617f4c33942f5.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(222, 24, '【分析】线材光纤化有什么优势', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">随着8K/4K影音应用与数码相机、摄影机相继挑战超高分辨率记录功能，对于现有的传输接口性能要求也越来越高，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">高速传输接口承载的资料传输量持续挑战铜缆线材的物理极限。</span><br/></span></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red;\">因此影音产品对于由8K/4K UHDTV带起的高速传输接口集成风潮，如HDMI/DP等，</span>虽在传输效能获得跃进式地大幅改善，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">但在长距离布设应用状况下，常用的</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: red; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\">铜芯特性并不利于长距离高速传送！</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211108/1636335218576936.jpg\" title=\"1636335218576936.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01dMrSkz1n0Pb52bJZi_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">铜缆传输速度与信号的辨识度都会因为距离拉长而受影响，如果搭配中继器等设备改善信号质量，会使传输成本暴增，同时对接口传输质量与稳定性也会造成影响！因此，<span style=\"caret-color: red; text-align: left;\">要求兼具传输距离与传输性能，AOC线材解决方案才能满足应用需求。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p></section></section><p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; outline: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">秋叶原作为影音连接线行业领军企业，下设秋叶原线缆研究院特研发出以光纤为传输介质，完美化解困扰业界远距离高速传输问题，实现</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;\">百米级以上</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; outline: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;\">超长距离传输视频信号的</span><span style=\"outline: 0px;\">秋叶原新一代光纤系列产品隆重面市，一起来看看吧！</span></span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; vertical-align: inherit;\"><strong>第三代光纤复合HDMI高清线</strong></p><p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211108/1636335189237358.jpg\" title=\"1636335189237358.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20211014160757.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">具有18Gbps的传输带宽，支持真4K、给你震撼3D视效，<span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\">画面显示时能做到色彩自然，明亮鲜明，细节层次感清晰，<span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">实现150米近乎0衰减，</span></span>打破超长距离信号传输衰减束缚。匠心呈现，“光”耀未来！</span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; vertical-align: inherit;\"><strong>蓝光系列光纤DP高清线</strong></p><p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211108/1636335169313439.jpg\" title=\"1636335169313439.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20211019165646.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">光电DP1.4 模组/AOC 产品采用光纤传输高速音视频信号，电子线传输低速控制信号，线材整体轻便，产品抗电磁干扰好，产品符合 DP1.4 协议规范，满足 8K 高清连接需求,传输距离最高可达150米无损耗传输。</span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; vertical-align: inherit;\"><strong>蓝光系列光纤DVI高清线</strong></p><p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211108/1636335137916469.jpg\" title=\"1636335137916469.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_202106181046314.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">光电DVI模组/AOC解决传统铜缆在DVI信号传输过程中信号衰减兼容性等问题，支持1080P，传输距离最高可达200米无损耗传输，高速信号通过4条多模光纤进行传输，具有良好的抗干扰性能，线材整体轻便，支持热插拔，低功耗，无需外部电源驱动。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><strong>蓝光系列光纤HDMI-DVI转换线</strong></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><br/></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">同时，秋叶原线缆研究院还攻破了200米超长距离</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">光纤</strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">HDMI-DVI<strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">、</strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">DVI-HDMI</strong></strong>转换线</strong></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">，可切实实现多接口不同使用需求，真正摆脱传输接口的限制。</span></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><br/></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211108/1636335089450287.jpg\" title=\"1636335089450287.jpg\" alt=\"HDMI.jpg\"/></section></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; vertical-align: inherit;\"><strong><br/></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; vertical-align: inherit;\"><strong>蓝光系列光纤DVI-HDMI转换线</strong></p><p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211108/1636335050823970.jpg\" title=\"1636335050823970.jpg\" alt=\"dvi.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">光纤</strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">HDMI-DVI<strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">、</strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">DVI-HDMI</strong></strong>转换线</strong></span>，支持1080P视频格式并向下兼容1080i/720P，最高传输速率1.65Gbps.传输距离最高可达200米无损耗传输，高速信号通过4条多模光纤进行传输，具有良好的抗干扰性能，线材整体轻便，低功耗，无需外部电源驱动。</span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">光纤与铜是两种常见的传输介质，两者都具备抗干扰性和良好的保密性，但对比之下，</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">光纤具有传输速率高、传输距离长、能耗低、使用方便等诸多优点，对于传输线缆光纤化需求也在逐渐增强。</span></span></p></section></p>', 1, 0, 1, 255, '2021-11-08 09:51:35', '2021-11-08 09:51:35', '2021-11-08 09:51:35', '2021-11-08 09:51:35', '/upload/image/20211108/6188829786a03.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN');
