, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 28px;\">网络面板对于布线系统来说，不是主要影响性能的产品部件，</span>但却<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 28px;\">是仅有的几个外露在墙体</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 1px;\">表面</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 28px;\">的产品之一，其性能与美观直接影响着整体布线的效果，要<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; outline: 0px;\">根据网线类别来选择与之对应的网络面板，才能达到其最佳传输性能。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><section data-role=\"title\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"105224\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 10px auto;line-height: 1.75em;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block;\"><section style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\"><section style=\"ba