or: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">惠秋总经理&amp;秋叶原研究院执行院长张涛先生代表集团公司为本届赛事闭幕致辞，首先<span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 34px; outline: none 0px !important;\">向所有的参赛运动员表示热烈的祝贺，</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 34px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); outline: none 0px !important;\">同时也向所有辛勤付出的裁判员和工作人员表示感谢。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 34px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); outline: none 0px !important; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: inherit;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211126/1637920084508793.jpg\" title=\"1637920084508793.jpg\" alt=\"3.webp.jpg\"/></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align: inherit;\"></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: #FF0000;\">惠秋总经理&amp;秋叶原研究院执行院长张涛先生</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: #FF0000;\">为本次闭幕式致辞</span></strong></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:inherit;line-height: normal;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">他表示参赛队员们工作、比赛两不误，经历了将近十天十几场的激烈角逐，完成了每一场比赛，充分展现了秋叶原人的精神风貌，每个队员敢于拼搏、奋勇向前的精神，都是可嘉的，都是值得称赞的。虽然比赛结果有名次，但是坚持到最后的每一个队员都是冠军，都拥有了强健的体魄和良好的心态，也是人生赛场上的冠军。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211126/1637920112421217.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1637920112421217.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211126/1637920112876583.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1637920112876583.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211126/1637920112257202.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1637920112257202.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p></section><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">篮球比赛是一项强身健体的运动，希望通过活动比赛带动大家平时多注重锻炼身体，因为有身体才有事业，有健康才有幸福。</span></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211126/1637920143365993.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1637920143365993.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211126/1637920143863334.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1637920143863334.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">篮球运动也是一个团体运动，每场球赛都要有组织、有策划，每个球员都有分工、有配合，只有团结合作才有可能赢得比赛的胜利。在工作中也是一样的，企业的各个部门，各个成员，缺一不可，通过团结互助，分工协作，才能共同完成各项经营指标和任务。&nbsp;</span></p><section><section style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;margin: 10px 0%;\"><section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;align-self: flex-end;margin-left: 10px;\"><section style=\"text-align: center;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;justify-content: center;\"><br/></section></section></section></section><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211126/1637920159753590.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1637920159753590.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211126/1637920159467614.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1637920159467614.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #3F3F3F;\">比赛结束了，但我们全年的工作任务还没有结束，在最后一个多月的时间里，我们要把在这次球赛中表现出来的饱满的激情、昂扬的斗志、拼搏的精神用到我们接下来的工作当中，冲刺最后一个月，圆满完成甚至超额完成全年的经营目标，将快乐，健康，拼搏，敬业的理念落实到生活和工作中，实现个人和企业的价值双赢。</span></span></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #3F3F3F;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>恭喜获奖队伍</strong></span></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section style=\"margin-top: -10px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;\"><section style=\"text-align: center;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\"\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #ff8124;\">&nbsp; 冠军：仓储物流、行政、采购&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);\">&nbsp;宝盛公司、水电工程联队&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211126/1637920175394932.jpg\" title=\"1637920175394932.jpg\" alt=\"11.webp.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">惠秋总经理&amp;秋叶原研究院执行院长张涛先生</span></strong></span></p><