tica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">劣质的网</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-indent: 32px; caret-color: red; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">线】</span></strong><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-indent: 32px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">会造成网络信号衰减，沿路干扰增加，使传输数据容易出错，因而会造成网速变慢、上网卡住、网页出错等情况。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-indent: 32px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-indent: 32px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20220112/1641953376542933.jpg\" title=\"1641953376542933.jpg\" alt=\"跳线.jpg\"/></span></p><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-indent: 32px; caret-color: red;\">除此之外，劣质网线的使用寿命很短，需</span><span style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 32px; caret-color: red;\">要经常重复购买，替换使用，<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">会给维修工作带来很大的困难，甚至在发生火灾时<span style=\"text-align: left;\">一旦烧着就会一直烧下去，</span></span></span><span style=\"widows: 1; caret-color: red;\">不仅<span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\">造成经济损失</span>，还危害到了我们的生命安全！</span></span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"widows: 1; caret-color: red;\"><br/></span></span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: #FF4C41;\"><strong><span style=\"widows: 1; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 32px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">总之，不论大家挑选什么线缆，都要充分发挥你那火眼金睛，</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: #FF4C41;\"><strong><span style=\"widows: 1; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 32px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">寻找靠谱的商家，买质量过硬的产品。</span></span></strong></span></section><p style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; text-indent: 32p